chunk-657e847e204ba05d49c9179cd844c800	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	26	800	-bat co. kinh cua nen van-hoc binh-dan mot luong sinh-khi sieu-nhien. Tinh-chat pho-bien cua dirc tin Cong-giao da di sau vao thanh-am tir-dieu cia dan-toc.\n\nD6 la mot hanh-trinh khong phai mot som mot chieu ma thanh-tuu. Trong thoi-ky so-khai dao Cong-giao ? VietNam, cac nha tho da gap nhieu noi kh6-khan di tim tir-ngr thich-dang de dien-dat nhung y-niem con moi-me, hoac vi khong sin co tir-ngur du nghia, hoac vi chua tham-nhuan dirc oni neo Keu Suou doy-sunx nlu-n tau oe-augs op uap u bat sau day, cac tir-ngir phien am ro-sa (Rosa) va thi-a (Gratia) chung-to mot su dung ngir chua dugc dieu-luyen nhap than :\n\n(9) Chuong Thi, Van Drc Ba, tap 1, Nhac doan Tieng Chuong Nam, Hanpi 1952, trang 30-31,\n\nTrang chau mo canh trang-sinh Trong cay curc tot curc lanh ro-sa Drgm nhnan vi-lo thi-a (gratia) Bon mia hoa no rum-ra la-lung (10)\n\nNhung but-phap Cong-giao Viet-Nam da tién-bo cung mot nhip vbi sy tru?ng-thanh cua giao hoi Viet-Nam. Thisi Sang-dinh Nguyen van Thich da thoat dich mot doan nhaca Phap-ngir va dura vao bai tho .loi chuc tung Durc Ba Maria. Nhung voi mot nghe-thuat nhap-than, thi-si da khong cho chung ta thay sy phong dich, chi nho tac-gia trung-dan-chung ta moi doan durgc xuat-xir :\n\n## LOI CHUC TUNG DUC BA MARIA\n\nRat Thanh Dong Trinh Me Chua Troi, Nguon an be ai tat khong voi. Thom thay mii hug noi thanh vang. Tot bay hoa huong chon goc gai. Nhut nguyet hai virng nhuong inh sing. Luoi nao ke xiet loi khen ngoi,\n\nThieu quang chin chuc kem mau tuoi. Rat Thanh Dong Trinh Me Chua Troi. (11)\n\nHai cau luan tren day thoat thai tir nguyen-van Phap-ngtr dan lam te-ngon (12) cho bai tho :\n\n- (10) J.M. Huy Hoang trich dan trong Trang Chau, Thanh-gia tai ban, Saigon, 1958, trang 4.\n- (11) Sang-dinh Nguyen van Thich, Sang dinh thi tap, phan I, trang 5. Dc san vi Chua so 239-240. Hue 1943. Bai tho tren day s6ng-tac nam 1911.\n- (12) V