ch-cyc nhur cac ton-giao khac. Theo su nhan-xet sau\n\nday cua Lé van Sieu, Nho-giao voi quan-niem so-menh, Phatgiao voi quan-niem nghiep-qua va Cong-giao voi quan-niem nhan-ai la α nhtrng cai vi-dai v, da di sau vao doi song tinh-than cua dan-toc :α Thyc la mot cai may-min la-lung het sirc khi ca ba nén ton-giao voi ba y-niem vi-dai ay duong nhao-nan tinh-than nguoi Viet-Nam tren	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:917cee4759cc04dc9ecda347631c189c", "default:extract:e0093cf49eb632f9ca0ff822336389df"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:29:56
