cau dung ngon-ngir van-tu de truyen-giao' vd nuoi-duong dirc tin.\n\nTheo nhirng nguon sir-lieu chac-chan, dao Cong-giao du-nhap xa-hoi Viet-Nam tir the-ky XVI. Ching ta cho rang vain-hoc Congsoy-upa pnb-noy yuow upyu ap p1 IAX (y-ayi ni ngp ipq opia\n\ntat nhien cia cong-cuoc truyén-giao. That ra, trong thé-ky XVI, cong-cupc truyen-giáo chura dugc to-chirc qui-mo va cung nhur chura co tac-pham van	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:5198dfc59d3caea644f5624318bb938b", "default:extract:bd031b576cc30fb65697351dd93724d3"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:04
