ren, trang\n6. 128-131.\n\nHoang Si-Khai, dau tien-si nam 1544, lam quan v6i nha Mac den churc Ho-bo Thugng-thu, noi tieng vé tho nom voi cac tap Sir-trinh-khuc, Tu-thoi-khuc, Tieu-doc lac-thu (9). Ban Tir-thoi-khuc (10) con dugc luru-truyen, gom 340 cau theo the song-that luc-bat. Xet ra	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:9ce4d0407ae6156f0c84778eecc57691", "default:extract:01bbbada6faf0a5b2e12e6449016ccfe"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:39
chunk-486ccca51b59360f41454b97fe7f2744	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	43	800	83.\n\nNhiem an lao cap tuan nam le, Khoa tan-mui (1631), de-nhi danh khoi\n\nDa hay than-mong yen bai, Ngoc lanh cing boi chuoc mai ra cong.\n\nTho quoc-am cua ong con luu-truyén bai Tho ha-tien va doi cau d6i (18).\n\nNhung nha tho trén day deu ky-thac trong tac-pham nguyen-vong thoat tuc, noi long hoai-co, la nhung chu-de thich-dung tr the-ky truoc. Hau het ho da tirng lam quan Dang Ngoai, hoic voi nha Mac, ho?c voi nha Lé trunghung. Truoc the-cuoc xoay-van nhanh-ch6ng, hau hét déu co phan-irng nhan-dinh giong nhu Nguyen Binh-Khiém.\n\nNha tho dac-sac cua tien-ban the-ky XVlI, chinh la Daoduy Tr (1572-1634) v6i sy-nghiep chinh-tri, quan-sy phuc vu chua Nguyen ? Dang Trong va voi cac thi-pham chr nom : Ngoa-long-cuong van, Tu-dung van va binh-thu Ho trurong khu co. Ay la nha van dau-tién cua Dang Trong va cung la imot nguoi trong the-he tien-phong roi bo Dang Ngoai de vao Dang Trong, nam-tién theo duong huong phat-trien tu nhien cua dan-toc.\n\nOng nguoi lang Hoa-trai, huyén Ngoc-son, tinh ThanhH6a, hoc gidi, con 6ng Dao-duy Han lam chirc chirc linhquan coi doi nir-nhac doi vua Le Anh-tong (1553-1573), vi quan-trurong theo thaph-kien xuong-ca vo-loai nen ong bi\n\n(18) Van dan bao giam, sdd trang 18; Tran trong Kim, sdd, trang 60.\n\ndanh hong trong ky thi huong. Ong phan chi, vao Dang uuo o quip-uua uap suo danu - is der nnu uo cho mot phu-gia lang Tung-chau, huyén Bong-son, phu Hoainhan, giong nhr Bach-ly-He doi Tan, lam tap Ngoa long curong van, tu vi minh. v6i Gia-cat Lugng. Quan kham-ly xur Qui-nhon Tran Durc-Hoa ga con gai va tién-cr Dao-duy Ti v6i chua Nguyen-phuc Nguyén (1613-l635). Ong dugc thudung lam Nha-uy Noi-Tan phong tuoc Loc-Khé Hau, coi-s6c viec noi ngoai quan-co, tham-ly quoc-chinh. Ong c6 cong trong viec xay dap don Truong-duc (? huyén Phong-Loc tinh Quangbinh) va luy Nhat-Lé (o cira Dong-hoi) tirc la Dinh-Bac truong-thanh, tuc goi la Luy Thay.\n\nTrong tap Ngoa long cuong van (19) dai 136 cau, Dao-duyTir ca tung thu thanh-nhan an-dat nhu Nguyen Binh-Khiem :\n\nThu vui bon thu them yeu, Kia ngur, no muc, äy tieu, nay canh. Hac gia truc cira nghe kinh, Goc ngan truc uon vo ve,\n\nTrái dang mau tham, thirc xanh phugng quy. Ngo dua hanh tia, hien khoe cuc vang.\n\nLoi tho binh-di nhung uyen-chuyén hon Bach-van quoc- ngur thi,	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:98770dcadddff35821d142a69f74a28c", "default:extract:52aad2f9dc2e88c8cb52e11c74f0825e"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:47
