n Viet xuat ban, Saigon 1950, trang 83.\n\nNhiem an lao cap tuan nam le, Khoa tan-mui (1631), de-nhi danh khoi\n\nDa hay than-mong yen bai, Ngoc lanh cing boi chuoc mai ra cong.\n\nTho quoc-am cua ong con luu-truyén bai Tho ha-tien va doi cau d6i (18).\n\nNhung nha tho trén day deu ky-thac trong tac-pham nguyen-vong thoat	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:5ebc6a67d63bdd9f32350c6f4a4eca54", "default:extract:c6f4f63b567563fc75d0b7d23b53cfe2"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:55
