chunk-84dc5defed032d8d76c3c47a78109273	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	44	800	nhu Nguyen Binh-Khiem :\n\nThu vui bon thu them yeu, Kia ngur, no muc, äy tieu, nay canh. Hac gia truc cira nghe kinh, Goc ngan truc uon vo ve,\n\nTrái dang mau tham, thirc xanh phugng quy. Ngo dua hanh tia, hien khoe cuc vang.\n\nLoi tho binh-di nhung uyen-chuyén hon Bach-van quoc- ngur thi, nhung dieu khac-biet dang n6i hon ca la xu-huong\n\n(9) Xem Van-hoc tap chf s6 4; Van-dan bao-giém quyen Ill sdd, trang 217223; Bui van Lang va To van Cau, Lich so Dao duy Tur, Ha-noi, Imp. Irung\n\nBac tan van, 1937.\n\nhoat-dong nhap the cua Dao-duy Tir. Trong luc Nguyen BinhKhiém ngoi nhin nuoc song Tuyét-giang voi doi mat thannhien ciia mot an si, Dao-duy Tir vugt trung-duong di tim mot dat hura. Trong khi phuc-vu ? Dang Trong, ong la nguoi cong-thin van-v? kiem-toan voi tai-dirc cua mot Khong-Minh ma ong da curc ta:\n\nCo phen xem tugng Thien-tao Dieu-xa la tran, phong-van ay do.\n\nKia ngoi khanh-turong, no sao quan than Co phen binh-phap dien tran, Co phen tho tii rugu ho, Thanh-y som chuic, ho-lo toi moi. (Ngoa-long-cuong van)\n\nNeu Ngoa-long-curong van la ngon gi6 khi-phach hao-hung tir Bac chuyénovao Nam thi tap Tur-dung van dai 336 cau la cai nhin tha-thiet huong ve giang-san cam-tu ma cira Tur-dung (tirc la cira Tu-hien ? Thira-thien) la mot bieu-tugng thanh-nha :\n\nVang nghe tieng mo gia le, Ngoi phien ben nao, rira tht sach khong. Dich nen canh la vo song, Hirng xui tao-khach dieu trung ngoi-khen.\n\nVira la tao-nhan mac-khach, vira la ke uu.thoi man-the, Dao-duy Tir da thyc-hien sy hoa dieu ky-thu gitura thi-van va hoat-dong.\n\nTro len la nhung tac-gia chinh-yeu trong khoang the-ky XVI va tién ban the-ky XVII. Muon dugc day-du, chung ta phai ke hai cuon truyén bang tho Duong-luat, chua tim ra tacmat. D6 la truyen To-Cong phung sir va truyen Bach-Vien Ton-\n\nCac (con biet-nhan la Lam-Tuyén ky-ngo).\n\nTruyen To-Cong phung sir (20) gom 24 bai tho Duongluat, la truyén Han Vu-Dé sai To-Vu di sur Hung-no va bi Hung-no cam tu 19 nam. Loi tho c6 nhurng chir co thinh-hanh thoi Le Mac. D?i chieu cot truyen vbi Viet-sur, chung ta thay doi Mac c6 Nguyen quang Bat di sir nha Minh cuing bi gir ? Tau 19 nam (1548-1566). Vua Mac Phuc-Nguyén nho chuyén To vu-phong cho ong la To quan-cong. Phai chang tap tho nay cua Nguyen quang Bat ?\n\nTruyén Bach-Vien Ton Cac (hay Lam-Tuyn ky-ng?) (21) gom 150 bai tho Du	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:4dd920856ca85a6828402fa6e7ee12f5", "default:extract:783da0b9c2ffdec34311da6a00527aff"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:29
chunk-50c635ede9f7ad13b8d7e6f56ac4f198	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	45	800	vbi Viet-sur, chung ta thay doi Mac c6 Nguyen quang Bat di sir nha Minh cuing bi gir ? Tau 19 nam (1548-1566). Vua Mac Phuc-Nguyén nho chuyén To vu-phong cho ong la To quan-cong. Phai chang tap tho nay cua Nguyen quang Bat ?\n\nTruyén Bach-Vien Ton Cac (hay Lam-Tuyn ky-ng?) (21) gom 150 bai tho Duong-luat, can cr vao chr co thi cung doan la xuat-hien thoi Le Mac. Truyén ké mot tien-no bi luu-day xuong coi tran lam con vugn trang biet n6i va di tu tién la Bach-Vien, man han luru-day Bach-Vien h6a thanh mot thieu-nir xinh-dep ket duyén voi Ton-Cac va sinh-ha dugc hai con. Sau khi vé coi tien, Bach-Vien nho chong con va xin\n\n(20) Xem Hoang Xuan Han, Nghiem Toan, sdd, trang 154-159.\n\n(21) Xem Hoang Xuan Han. Nghiem Toan, sdd, trang l6l-178; Le Tuyen, Banthe va hien tuong trong thi ca Viet-Nam, hubng doi thoai ve hien hiu gbu-Ay ngo-yoig en gbu-<y uaanj-we7 !eoyi ua! 5eo buos1 onbu uos in trong Dc-San Dai hoc Su-pham, tap l, nien-kh6a 1960-196l, Hue trang 83.110.\n\nphép xuong tran tai-hgp. Cau chnyén ket-thuc khi Ton-Cac dau Trang lam quan tai Kinh.\n\nThat kh6 ma trinh-bay day-du 150 n?m van-hoc trong mot tiét-muc cua mot chuong sach. De b-khuyét, chung ta thi dua ra nhirng nhan-dinh dai-cuong ve tanh.cach van-hoc cia thoi-ky nay.\n\n## 3. Tong quan ve van-hoc the-ky XVl va tien-ban the ky xvll.\n\nTruyén-thong ton-trong dao-ly cua thoi ky truoc van duoc duy-tri nhung khong dugc hién-minh nhr truoc. Khuynh huong giao-huan chi-ph?i ngay ca nhtng de-muc c6 tinh-chat tu-tinh. Tinh-cam ca-nhan bi don-ep dubi uy-lyc cua doan-the, cua cac giao-dieu. Du thoa-hiep voi chinh-quyén hay -iun ouo yunu-uiiq suon-nuo uea euu oeo 'ep-ueuu no-ug np do x' the cua minh hon la giai-bay tryc-tiep tam-tu.\n\nTuy nhien bau khong-khi van-hoc tram-tinh ay da bat dau xao-xuyén vi mot ngon-ngr van-chuong moi tao nén nhurng net di-biet bat-dong.\n\n## a) Mot ngon-ngi van-chuong moi\n\nVe hinh-thrc chung ta nhan thay no-lyc tim kiém mot ngon-ngu van chuong moi. Loi dung-ngir chu-trong den danhtir dac-biet cua thoi-dai. Tac-pham cua Le Durc-Mao, Nguyén Binh-Khiem, Dao-duy Tir gom c6 nhieu chtr co, nhieu thécach dien-dat dac-biet thoi Lé, Mac.\n\nVe the-cach, loi hat a dao dugc pho-bien vbi Bai hat ch	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:e6ea5ef2b93983d9c202b91b9545a1ee", "default:extract:2869bf30115bfc30ec72a40395c57c21"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:30
chunk-4c8a5253557e55c6047840c7ed1342a2	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	46	800	tim kiém mot ngon-ngu van chuong moi. Loi dung-ngir chu-trong den danhtir dac-biet cua thoi-dai. Tac-pham cua Le Durc-Mao, Nguyén Binh-Khiem, Dao-duy Tir gom c6 nhieu chtr co, nhieu thécach dien-dat dac-biet thoi Lé, Mac.\n\nVe the-cach, loi hat a dao dugc pho-bien vbi Bai hat chuc ldng cua Le Durc-Mao. Loi luc-ngon-thé, thinh-hanh doi Hongdirc, con dugc irng-dung trong Bach-Vin quoc-ngi thi nhung xao-nhang trong tien-ban the-ky XVII. Loi sorg-that luc-bat manh-nha trong Bai hat chut lang, da bat dau on-dinh trong Tu thoi khuc vinh cua Hoang Si-Khai, bao hieu tinh-chat dieu-luyén cua Chinh.phu ngam sau nay :\n\nGi6 hiu-hiu goi cao song bac, Ta moi sau, chang mic chut lo\n\nTréo chan, nam ech, ngay pho Ngam hay chang khac nguoi vua Hy, Hoang.\n\nLoi phu nom da tr? nén thuan-nha, bao-hieu nhung tac- pham dac-sac doi sau. Tich-cu ninh-the phu dang ke la mot bai phu c6 gia-tri nghe-thuat.\n\nMuon nhan thay phan d6ng gop moi-me cua the-ky XVI va tién-ban the-ky XVII thiét-tu?ng chung ta c6 the so-sanh but-phap cua Nguyen Trai (the-ky XIV) voi but-phap cua\n\nNguyen Binh-Khiém (th-ky XVI) va Dao-duy Tr (the-ky XVI1)\n\nNguyen-Trai con ly-luan vé canh nhan, con bi am-anh boi lich-sir trong khi nhin thien-nhien :\n\nBa-Di nguoi rang thanh la thu Nhan-tir ta xem ngat ay lé (Quc-am thi tap, bai 48)\n\nNguyen Binh-Khiem va Dao.duy Tt hoan toan hba dieu nhap than trong coi ty-nhién :\n\nThu in mang truc, dong in giá, Rupu den coi cay ta se nhap,\n\nXuan taim ho sen, ha taim ao. Nhin xem phu-quy tura chiem-bao.\n\n(Bach-van qu?c ngur thi)\n\n-- Dich nén canh la vo song Hirng xui tao khach dieu trung ngoi-khen. (Tu-Dung van)\n\n## b) Nhan-thirc di-bigt, van-chuong da-dang.\n\nSu phong-phu vé noi-dung con ro-ret hon nura. Thoi-the loan-lac dat cac nha van truoc mot sy lya-chon nhieu khi dén dau-kh?. Ti viec xac-dinh lap-truong chinh-tri hoic hop tac voi nha Mac, hoac trung-thanh voi nha Lé, hoac nan-na doi thoi ? Dang Ngoai, hoac durt-khoat voi hien-tai di vao Dang Trong lap nghiep, cac nha van da de cap den nhung lya chon. Phung Khac-Khoan mo ve mot coi thien-thai vinh-. phuc trong Ngu-phi nhap Dao nguyen truyen, nhung tir tiéngibi nang Bach-thi cua truyen Lam-tuyen ky ngo van huong vé\n\ntran-gian trong tinh yéu doi lra :\n\nTrot mang mot nghia cing nguyen-uoc, Chi de doi noi luong khat khao.\n\nBui Vinh	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:8d669b4076263dbe7465af244deb764b", "default:extract:6446a09b805422fff5197d35be8356f2"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:37
chunk-45dbce8a8bc3f0c9c0f579894dc250c3	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	47	800	ya chon. Phung Khac-Khoan mo ve mot coi thien-thai vinh-. phuc trong Ngu-phi nhap Dao nguyen truyen, nhung tir tiéngibi nang Bach-thi cua truyen Lam-tuyen ky ngo van huong vé\n\ntran-gian trong tinh yéu doi lra :\n\nTrot mang mot nghia cing nguyen-uoc, Chi de doi noi luong khat khao.\n\nBui Vinh tha thiet voi cung vang dien ngoc nha Mac trong Cung trung bao huän, nhung Nguyen Hang quyet tam thoit tuc hu?ng nhan trong Tich cur ninh the phu va Nguyen Binh-Khiem\n\nroi-b? chinh-truong tr? vé ton tam duong tanh ? Bach-van am :\n\nDanh toqi cong thanh huu hi huru Dang nhan the co nhat hu chau (22)\n\nNhung Dao.duy-Tr lai khang-khai hon, di vao Dang\n\nTrong thyc-hien triét-ly hanh-dong theo guong Khong-Minh.\n\nHba cong dang chuoc lq nhuing Gio ngan Xich Bich thbi lun nguy-binh\n\n(uea Suo0-suon-eogN)\n\nNhung sy lura-chon la tlm-kiem nhr the chirng-t? rang vin-hoc Viet-Nam da do sinh-thanh chuyén huong. Trong tinh-trang coi-m? nay, nén van.hoc cong-giao dugc phat-sinh va dugc chip-nhan nhr la mot iroc-vong cua thoi-dai, thoaman sy tim-kiem va lra-chon cua mot so nguoi khong con tim thay sy binh-an trong khuon-kh6 tam-giao co-truyen va durgc on phu&c an-nghi trong Thien-Chua.\n\n## III.- TINH-HINH TRUYEN-GIAO\n\nTheo nghi-sir, dao Cong-giao du-rhap nu?c ta tir thoi cac thanh Tong-do, c6 sach chép rang thoi thanh To-ma tong-do -auonun ogo oau 1p ep ap-uou os nou 'op-uy ? ogia uaknn\n\n- (22) Djch nghia: nhir the cung goi la cong toai danh thanh roi day, thoi the cung nén thoi. Viec doi ph6 mac cho con thuyén voi voi no lenh denh muon den dau thi den ma ta tim lai cai thii vui cua ta. Ban dich cua D6 Nam, Danh-nhan Hai durong, Vll, Nam-Phong tap-chi, top XXXlll s6 160.\n\nthuyen den truyén-giao cho nguoi Viet. Si-Nhiep da dung den tho voi hinh Thanh Gia trong dinh ? quan Curu-chan (Thanhhba), con chau cuia ong gitr dao cho den nguoi chau nam doi thoi (23).\n\n-a g o nu u  o nhan. Sur-lieu hien nay chi xac-nhan rang ke ti the ky XVI, dao Cong-Giao dugc truyen giang & Viet-Nam.\n\n1. Thé-ky XVl : viéc truyen-giáo trong thoi ky phoithai.\n\nDén the-ky XVI, thuong-thuyén Bo-dao-nha da di lai ? An.do duong va Nam-hai. Nam 1510, thanh Goa (An-Do) thuoc de-quoc Bo. Nam áy, nguoi Bo goi phai - bo den Thailan. Nam 1514 ho dén Quang-Dong (Trung-hoa) va sau d6 ho di het bo be Bac	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:c026786d9e6652cc98053ff63c4a1df8", "default:extract:cae02d40aee31e3ef7b1edb8b9b33cde"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:41
chunk-4fc9aefb3814ed50d6662a61efcb3fc8	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	49	800	nhung cha da di khap tinh tü Bac chi Nam, ma cha con vugt ranh-gioi tinh va den vung Ba-ria ? Nam-Viet\n\n(25) Nguyen Phuong, Cha Dc lo vbi sy thanh lap Giso-hoi Cong-giao Viet Nam, in trong Dai-hgc, s8 19, thang 2 nm 1661 trang 71-87.\n\n(26) C.A. Poncet, L'un des premiers annamites, sinon le premier converti au. catholicisme, in trong BAVH nam XXVlll, thang 1-3 nam 1941 tr 81-99.\n\nroi tir day di Quang Dong》 (27) Theo tai-lieu nay, thi tru6c khi Chan-lap chinh thurc sap-nhap lanh-th? Viet-Nam vao w 9 2p zA 10nau IX 4Y 2un n Aeu '1AX y 2y1 1on) Ha tién ngay nay, dén do c6 the xem d6 la lanh-th Viet-\n\nNam.\n\nTiep theo cha Gaspar de Santa, duoi doi Vua Lé Anhtong (1548-1556), hai cha dong Da-Minh dén dät Viet-Nam (1563), hoat-dong truyen-giao trong 10 nam, sau bi truc-xuat nén phai tr? vé Ao-mon.\n\nNam I1580, hai cha dong Da-minh, tir Malacca dén truyén- giao ? Quang-nam : cha Luis de Fonseca nguoi Bo va cha Grégroire de la Motte nguoi Phap. Chua Nguyen Hoang ra lénh bat. Cha Luis de Fonséca bi giet dang khi hanh le va cha Gregroire de la Motte bi tir thuong.\n\nTheo tai-lieu cac dong tu, vao khoang cuoi the-ky XvI, nha Le va nha Mac c6 ngo y xin cac giao-si den giang dao trong nuoc.\n\nNam 1570 Vua Le Anh-tong, sau khi tiép nhan mot burc hoa cuoc phan-xet chung do mot linh-muc dong Phan-xi-co dang tang, c6 moi linh-muc den giang-dao, nhung vi thieu linh-muc nen loi yéu-cau khong dugc thoa-man. Nha vua c6 yéu cau Toa Giam-Muc ? Ao-mon song cuing khong c6 ket-qua.\n\nNim 1580, theo linh-muc Ordonez de Cevallos (28) MaiHoa cong-chua, chi vua Lé The-tong, bay gio gir chirc Nhiépchinh, cung c6 yéu-cau cac Toa Giam-Muc Ao-mon va Goa goi cac thira sai dén dat Viet. Chinh cha Ordonez de Cevallos dä rira toi cho Mai-Hoa cong-chua. Ba c6 lap mot ntr-tu-vien ? An-truong (Thanh-hoa). Theo sy khao-ciru cua giao-si Poncet, chuyen Mai-Hoa cong chia ma Ordonez Cevallos goi Flora Maria va sir ta goi la Ba chua Chem chuyen c6 that. Hien nay, gan An-truong c6 mot noi goi la nén Tho, c6 1e 1a noi xua kia da xay nha tho nir-tu-vien. Lai c6 mot cai gieng tuc goi la giéng Gia-To, c6 le do ba Mai-Hoa cong-chua da cho dao lén, nén goi nhu the de nho on Ba (29).\n\nNam 1581	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:347de176b58c11ebfba371cd866aceee", "default:extract:832928ff38a63099a97f245c658caf72"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:53
