g chung ta da thay, viec truyén-giao trong the-ky\n\nXVI & Viet-Nam dang ? trong thoi-ky phoi-thai, thiéu han mot he-thong to.chirc chat-che, mot ke-hoach lién-tuc nen ketqu? khong dugc my-man nhr trong thoi-ky sau d6 cac cha Dong Tén phu-trach.\n\n## 2. Tien-ban the-ky XVll : Viec truyen-giao do giao-si Dong Ten phy-trach.\n\nNam 16l4, Nhat-ban cam dao va truc xuat cac giao si Dong Ten ra khoi nuoc. Mot so, dong giao	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:94d637337c2bfd00874c1a250cbddc82", "default:extract:1496b3c5c574ff9dc664f2cb91748e6a"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:58
chunk-9673d0efbac78421566be895beb4d5f2	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	48	800	oi ky phoithai.\n\nDén the-ky XVI, thuong-thuyén Bo-dao-nha da di lai ? An.do duong va Nam-hai. Nam 1510, thanh Goa (An-Do) thuoc de-quoc Bo. Nam áy, nguoi Bo goi phai - bo den Thailan. Nam 1514 ho dén Quang-Dong (Trung-hoa) va sau d6 ho di het bo be Bac-Viet, nhu cac ong Fernandez Perez nam 1516 va Duarte Coelho nam 1524 ; ong Antonio de Faria vao ving Fa-nang va chu y dén Hai-pho (Hoi-an). Nhung cuoc tiépxuic nhu the chinh la co-hoi de linh-muc tuyén-uy'cac thuong thuyén αtiép-xuc voi dan dia-phuong cung giang cho ho vé\n\nThién-Chua giao》 (24)\n\nSir-lieu Viet-Nam chép : α Nam Nguyén-hoa nguyén-nien doi vua Lé Trang-tong nha Le (1533-1548) c6 mot nguroi Tay-phuong (duong-nhan) tén la I-né-khu di duong be len vao giang dao Gia-to ? lang Ninh-cuong, Quan-anh thuoc\n\n(23) Xem Truong-vinh Ky, Cours d'histoire d'Annam, cuon I, Saigon, 1875\n\ntrang 27.\n\n(24) Géographie d' Earisi, ban dich tieng Phap, trang 84.\n\nhuyen Nam-chan (tirc Nam.truc) va o mien lang Tra-li thuoc huyén Giao-thuy (ve mien Nam.dinh, Thai-binh, Ninh-binh ngay nay 》 (25).\n\nI-ne-khu la phien-am tiéng Inigo, chac la mot giao-si cong- giao tir Ma-lai den.\n\nGia-pha ho Do ? Thanh-H6a co ghi chép Do Hung-Vien theo dao Hoa-lang tirc lang dao Cong·giao. Theo sy suy-luan cua Giao-si Poncet, Do Hurng-Vien tr? lai dao Cong-giao trong mot.chuyén cong-du hoac & Ao-Mon hoac ? dao Celebes αtrong khoang hau ban the ky XVIn duoi trieu vua Lé Anhtong (1556-1573) (26) va c6 1e 1a mot trong nhrng nguoi dau tién theo dao Cong-giao ? nuroc ta.\n\nNguon sir-lieu ngoai-quoc cing xac-nhan rang viec truyén giao khoi dien ? Viet-Nam tir the-ky XVI.\n\nTheo giao-si Marcos Gispert, αvi thira sai Au chau, theo chung ta het, den dat Viet giang dao ttuoc tien la giao si Gaspar de Santa thuoc dong Da-minh, quoc tich Bo-dao-nha. tinh dong Santa Cruz (Goa). Nam 1550, duoi trieu Lé Trungtong (1548-1556), cha