chunk-f9bdd729a8f9d8cae5e2e01f2241d6fa	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	63	800	-5-l622 tai Nuoc Man\n\n(9) Xem Thanh-lang, sdd, trang 19\n\n(10) Nguyen Khac Xuyen, Chung quanh van-de thanh-lap chir quoc-ngi vao nam 1645, VHNS loai m6i, s6 48 théng 1-2 nam 1960 trang 2.\n\nuoa -oa i on n un (o-) Ro-ma du6i ky hieu ARSI Jap. Sin. 68a ff 1-4 va 6-10, danhtir Han-Viet Thien-chu da durgc phien-am la Thienchu viét lien nhau, khong c6 däu mi () va dau hoi (7).\n\nQua hai van-liéu ngan-ngúi trén day, chung ta c6 the phong doan ma khong sai-lam bao nhieu la giao-si Buzomi dang -auo mau-uou nea uel au-auonyd rey enia np-op Viet-Nam.\n\nPhuong-the thur nhat Ia phien-am hay dung chinh danh-tir. Au-chau ghep vao tieng Viet nhur truong-hgp dao Christiam. Ket-qua la chung ta c6 nhung tir-ngir lai Viet lai Au, khong thich-hop voi thanh-van va nhac-dieu co-htru cua tieng Viet.\n\nPhuong-the thr hai la nhap-tich nhirng danh-tir goc Han, tao nén nhirng danh-tir Han-Viét nhur truong hgp Thien-chu. Két-qua la chung ta c6 nhirng tir-ngi cau-tao theo lé-l6i tunhien cua Viet-ngir, khong lam cho nhung nguoi tham-nhuan nho-hoc ph?i bo-ngo mat cong tim hiéu nhu truong-hop nhitrng danh-tir nguyén-lai & cac ngon-ngi Tay-phuong.\n\n## IV.- QUOC-THU .CUA CHUA TRINH TRANG (1627)\n\nNam 1627, cac giao-si Alexandre de Rhodes va Pedro Marquez. Y ? nn-nn daud.ouo (s9l-zi) sueii yuii enuo oonp Cho (Ha-noi) dé truyén-giao.\n\nNhan dip thuong-thuyén Bo-dao-nha tr? ve Ao-mon, chua\n\nTrinh Trang co goi cho cha Phu-tinh Dong Tén mot quoc-thu.\n\nkhic trén mieng dong la. Van-kien ngoai-giao nay gay mat Imiy hang dau, hien luru-trir tai Thu-vien Vatican, Fonds\n\nBarberini, Orient 158 (11).\n\nNguyén-van chr Han, phien-am va dich ra Viet-ngu nhur sau:\n\n... Tiéu nghi do binh cong thurgng, ty nhi gido si sai ciru giao. Kim phuc tuyen nhi giao si tinh thirc thien van dia ly chi hoc nghe bon quoc xien minh thanh giao, nghiem thap gioi tong tap tqi tam, linh ky boi thuc 