am-tu cuia giao-huru nhiet-thanh, v&i hinh-thirc thuan-tuy dan-toc, gian-di chat-phac ma van taonha doan-trang. * **\n\nTir cuon Do-toc gia-pha den birc thur cia Bento Thién va Igessio Van Tin, chung ta vira nhin lai tien-trinh cua ngon-ngr Cong-giao Viet-Nam trong khoang gan 150 nam.\n\nTruroc khi cac cha Dong Ten dén truyén-giao, nghia la tir nim 1615 tr? vé truoc, chung ta gap nhung tir-ngir, nhing kiéu n6i chua du kha-nang dien-dat thyc-chat Cong-giao. Ngontir luc bay gio chua di kip noi-dung muon pho-dien.\n\nNo lurc truyén-giao cia cac Cha Dong Tén trong tien-ban thé	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:2ef09502b19314788528b0be4efd95e2", "default:extract:0282c87ef78de68bf4bdf3335506762b"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:30
chunk-2b7afe18b3d99754532753412788d863	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	72	800	chung ta nhan' thay su than-trong cua cac thira-sai trong cong viec chuyéndich ngon-ngir than-hoc Au-chau sang Viet-ngir. Phan dong vi y-nghia cia cac danh-tir va van-phap dac-biet cua ngonngir nuoc ta. Thai-do than-trong va no-lurc hoc-hoi äy la nhrng yéu-to anh-huong dén sy hinh-thanh cua ngon-ngu Cong-giao Viet-Nam.\n\nChu-dich cua cac giao-si la tao nén mot cong-thirc dugc qi nguoi hieu ro day-du y-nghia cua bi-tich rura toi va tindicu Thien-Chua Ba Ngoi. Ve van-tir, cac giao-si khong ngai nla.\n\n-ud oi n  om a ngir c6 1e vi cac giao-si chua tim ra dugc mot danh-ti tuongxirng. Phai dgi dén thoi-ky truyen-giao sau moi c6 danh-tir Chua Thanh Than voi noi-dung dung voi tin-ly Cong-giao. Phuong chi, khuynh-huong dung nguyén-van danh-tir ngoai. quoc dang thang-the ? tien-ban the-ky XVI1.\n\nVIII.- THU CUA BENTO THIEN VA IGESSIO VAN TIN GOI CHO GIAO-SI FILLIPPO DE MARINI (1659)\n\nFilippo de Marini la mot giao-si Dong Tén dén Dang\n\nNgoai nam 1647 va bi truc-xuat nam 1658.\n\nTheo Hoang Xuan-Han trong bai Mot vai vin-kin bang quoc-am tang-trir ? Au-chau (24), Vien bao-tang Dong Tén ? Ro-ma con gir mot burc tho cua Bento Thien goi cho giao si Filippo de Marini d, nam 1659 va mot birc thr cuia Igessio Van Tin g?i cho giao-si Filippo de Marini, cu?i thu de α mong 2 thang 9 Dirc Chua Troi ra doi 1659 )(nguyénvin la: mung hay thanh chinh D.C.J. ra doy mot nghin sau muoi nam muoy chinh) (25).\n\n(24) Dai hoc s8 10, thang 7 1959 trang 108-119.\n\n(25) Theo tai lieu chup hinh cua L.M. Va.Khanh-Tuong·\n\nNgoai ra con c6 mot bai dai ke sir-ky dia-du phong-tuc nuoc ta ma Hoang Xuan-Han cho Ia α Bento Thien lam va grl cho Filippo de Marini nam l659 de giao-si nay viét sach Historia et relatione del Tunchino nam 1665 v.\n\nHai birc thu n6i trén ghi dau mot giai-doan tien-trien cua ngon-ngtr Cong-giao Viet-Nam.\n\nDoan ch6t cua birc thur cia Bento Thien nhu sau:\n\nu O'n dirc Chua Bloy bla' cao cho that doy doy. Bai nhiey mloy toy chep thang muroy i Igrega ma thur nai thi ngai Le Bd Thinh Davia cu on Thinh Miganto tir vi dao, toy lai on thai ld cha vi thuong den con ci toy xin cha cho quen lam chi.\n\nTir Dirc Chuia Jesu ra doy cho den rai mot nghin sau tram nam muoy chin nam.\n\nBento Thien toy ta nha Thai. )\n\nTrong birc thu cua Igessio Van Tin, voi but.phap cing ging nhu cua Bento Thien, chung ta gap tir-ngi sau : that ca, (thay ca) bon dai (	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:d04296ba9a22dbb3a6ed85af3b0c9b51", "default:extract:c468d0f383bf50ee822bee96f72839f6"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:31
chunk-64b55a93de46c4124378fd905f9ee7c7	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	75	800	ien than lai bao Thanh Mau Maria nai nhan Thanh Than thy dung thinh chung dong dao khan ky Thien Chua, di Chua th6nh sung ph6 u thau dang linh hon (hay la linh hon mo). Ti than pham do Thien than chi b6o di chi Thien Chua tir giang duyng gia, nhan ky kho nan cap ky thap tur Thanh gia hanh dai ur phuc sinh chi vinh phuc, diec vi thi than dang\n\nChua Kirixito Amen..\n\nThien Chua hong huu vinh dir than dang giai yeu. Amen.\n\n## CHUONGIII\n\n## VAN-HOC CONG-GIAO TRUYEN KHAU\n\nbang hinh-thai truyén-khau, voi nhirng tac-pham dugc congdong chap-thuan lam cua chung dén do kh6 tim ra tac-gia. Van-hoc Cong-giao Viet-Nam cing the. Nhung l6i hung-bien ton-giao, nhurng bai ca-nhac phung-vu da la nhung hinh-thirc pho-dien truyen-khau di truoc nhirng tac-pham thanh van.\n\n## I.- CA-NHAC CONG-GIAO BINH-DAN\n\nTrong nhirng yeu-to cau-tao nen van-hoc truyen-khau Viet Nam, cac hoc-gia thuong nhan manh nhac-dieu co-hiu cua cua tieng Viet va tinh-than mo-mong cua nguoi Viet. Nhrng cau ca-dao thi-vi, nhirng dieu dan-ca phong-phu, chinh la nhurng tuyet-pham nho-nh? durgc du-luan tan-thu?ng-\n\nNhung nhan-dinh trén day c6 the ap-dung doi voi cac'tac pliam ca-nhac cong-giao binh-dan, xuat-hien ·? Viet - Nam tir lbi binh-minh cua dao Cong-giao ? Viet-Nam, nhu but-tich cia nhieu vi thira-sai duong thoi ghi-nhan.\n\nNoi guong thanh Phanxico Xavie, vi tong-do mien DongA, cac thira-sai chu-truong thich-irng viec truyén-giao voi cac nén van-minh co-truyen ban-xur. Nguoi chu-xuong thoi-danh dip 9 5p (09l - 611) ouue o1pux 1s-o  yu di quan-sat cac co-s? truyén-giao ? Trung-Dong va Vien-Dong Chu-trurong khon-ngoan nay dugc cac giao-si thurc-hien & Ando voi giao-si Nobili ? Trung-hoa voi cac giao-si Ruggieri va Ricci\n\n## 1. -- Ca-nhac phyng-vy binh-dan.\n\nO Viet-Nam vao dau the-ky XVIl, phong-trao ca-nhac phung-vu binh-dan chirng t? no-lurc thich-nghi viéc truyéngiao voi cac gia-tri tich-cuc cua van-hoc Viet - Nam. Kinh nguyen va mau-nhiem cua dao Cong-giao'da dugc trinh-bay theo the-dieu co-truyén de giao-dan cam-nhan de-dang hon. Trong thien khao-luan Nén van-chuong cong-giao ve Phanxico Xavie tai Viet-Nam (l) Georg Schurhammer da ghi-nhan :\n\n(1) Georg Schurhammer, Annamitish Xavierius Literatur, bai dong trong quyen Missionwissenschaftlich Studien, Aix la-ChaPeele, 1951 trang 300-314	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:f8feb936506c5f7eebb8b367350b3a03", "default:extract:e005a31ef7c21ca6732390ea1312ea36"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:35
chunk-2a7eff5d1ea7da964a7d9c11dc521a02	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	79	800	dugc sang-tac theo cac the tho dan-toc nhur n6i 16i, luc bat, thuong gom nhurng tir-nhr co, hay nhing kiéu n6i dac-biet cuia Cong-giao. Cung-dieu rat phong-phu dac-sac co bai la nhtrng dieu ca ly co-truyén, c6 bai durgc α cau-tao theo mot duong l6i riéng-biet, khac xa nhung dieu co-truyén kia 》 (16)\n\nSau day la mot bai van Durc Ba (17) theo the n6i l6i rat gan loi hat n6i ve phuong-dien dung van lien-tiép va yeu-van :\n\n(15) Chuong Thi, Van Durc Ba, Tap I, nhac doan Tiéng Chuong Nam, Ha-\n\nnoi, 1952. trg 3-4.\n\n(16) Xem bai cua H.V.H, bdd, nhat bao Xay-Durng, ngay 6-6-1965.\n\n(17) Trich dan theo Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, Tim hieu Ciao-nhac, Tinh Viet, Hanoi 1952, trg 35-36. Téc gia ghi-chép tir mieng mot ba trum da co tubi, 《 thoi con xuan sac, ba la tay ca-van bac nhat n.\n\nGi6 huan-phong thoang qua vuon cam, Canh thanh-hoa sac da sang he. Tram thir hoa dua no tir be, Hoa thanh-lich chi ve nhan-dirc. Mirng Diurc Ba nhur hoa ngu saic, Mui thom-tho nuc chon tran-gian, Chir dong-trinh ghi tac da vang. Guong trung-nghia khap nhan-hoan lap-linh\n\n······\n\nChing con nay tien hoa phung-su,\n\nGiai tom long xich tur bay lau, .O'n ga-xa van doi tren dau, Tay dang hat may cau cau-nguyen.\n\nGa-xa, phien-am la-ngi gratia nghia la duyén-dang, on nghia la mot tir-ngr co. Trong nhing cau van theo the luc bat sau day, chung ta cing gap nhing ti-ngir c6 nhu mon-may, Chua Deu. Thiet-tu?ng c6 the can-cir vao nhing tir-ngr ay de an-dinh soan-nién cia cac bai van d6 la thuoc thoi khoi-thuy cua Giao-hoi Cong-giao Viet-Nam :\n\n- 一 Cung con mon-may pham-hen\n- Lay on Diurc Me Chua Déu 一\n- Chung toi trong-cay cing keu-van Ba.\n\nKhuon-kho the tho luc-bat thuong durgc noi rong de thich-urng v6i nhrng 1e-16i dac-biet cua nen ca-xuong Viet-\n\nNam, nhu ngan-nga nhan liy hay dy-dien (anticipatton), nghia\n\nla dua ra truoc mot so chir cia cau tho. Vi-du churng-minh day dugc trich-din theo sur sau Chuong-Thi (18) :\n\nDong taim long (i) thanh, Chung toi dang tam long (i) thanh,\n\nMay loi van phic (i) may nganh (a) may nganh Man-coi (i).\n\n<!-- image -->\n\nVan-hoc-sir va nhac-sir Viet-Nam khong the bo qua truyén-thong ca-nhac phung-vu binh-dan. Gan day cong cuoc suru-tam (19) va phat-trién (20) nen ca-nhac ay da dug	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:a33002767f8b5f7c5d335312560c5d9b", "default:extract:380ffd08fbe7b83d699746fa7a17ac6e"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:38
