phyc cac nho-si.\n\nTrong luc giao-si Francesco Buzomi truyen-giao ? Quinhon, giao-si Francesco de Pina hoat-dong ? Quang-nam.\n\nLuic bay gio c6 mot lao-nho c6 uy-tin ? Quang-nam. Cha Pina von da tinh-thong Viet ngi va am-turong van-h6a VietNam, tim cach giao-thiep voi cu de dua cu tr? lai dao that. Giao-si nhan thay cu c6 tinh-than phuc-ly, muon tim hiéu dao Cong giao nhung dang con rut-re do-dy vi tinh bao-thu. Sau khi nghe giao-si Pina thuyét-g	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:c54dd402f091e642809db3ade5371af3", "default:extract:555f6f2e4c666115088c82158eaf02f8"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:49
