moi nguoi trong xr ) (37). Gioi quan lai durong-thoi da chu-y va chiu anh-hu?ng cac thi-\n\n(33) M. Ferreira, sdd. 192\n\n(34) M. Ferreira, 192-193, 187-188 : Il Japsin 73, 170, 175. A. Launayy 510-520\n\n(35) Japsin 75, 171\n\n.(36) Georg Schurhammer, bdd. trg. 153\n\n(37) Georg Schurhammer, bdd. trg. 153\n\npham cua Gioan Thanh-minh (38) chinh Chua Nguyén-phuc\n\nLan (1635-1658) khi nghe ong ngam tho cung phai khen (39).\n\n*\n\n**\n\nVan-pham cua Gi	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:4c9e1b2b8b763fc9119ed20c810ce275", "default:extract:891ed83565dba8958fee71ab59413dfb"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:37
chunk-89823a25d82b96c2f2e2747284e1ee86	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	106	800	ien quy-bau giup chung ta tim hiéu phuong-phap giang dao, ngon-ngtr cong-giao trong tien-ban the-ky XVII.\n\n(27) sdd. oan thi 7 : Ong Thanh I-na-xu di hoc cung chju kho o thanh Sai-lo-na. Phan trich-dan chinh-van deu phien-dien tir nguyen-van chu Nom.\n\n## II.— GIOAN THANH-MINH (1588 - 1663).\n\nGiao-sir chep ong la mot giao-hiu viét van nom conggiao nhung hien nay chung ta biét rat it ve ly-lich.va chua suu-tam durgc van-pham.\n\n## 1.- Tieu-sur\n\nVe nha van nay. co sach chep la Joao Ketlam (28), c6 sach. chép la Joao Vuang (29). Ketlam la que-quan cua nguoi me, 1 mot dia-danh ma chung ta chua tim durgc vi-tri trong ban-do Viet-Nam. Joao la ten thanh. viét theo loi Bo-dao-nha tirc la. Gioan. Thanh-minh la sinh-quan, mot xa tai quan Binh-son, tinh Quing-ngai. Nay chung ta goi nha van nay bang GioanThanh-minh gom ten thanh va sinh-quan, la theo mot l6i goi thuan-tuy dan-toc, vira xung tuoc-hieu vitra nhac-nh? den quehucng nhu kiéu chung ta van goi Nguyen Khuyén la Tam-. nguyen Yen-do, Nguyen Cong-Trir la Uy-vien turong-cong.\n\nCha me Gioan Thanh-minh la nguoi ngoai-dao. Than-sinh (ie) yur euon tyu nu oeq oea (o) uoi onuo uenb iou el ong len muoi lam tu6i, ong gia-nhap cira Khong san Trinh,\n\n- (28) Xem : Georg Schurhammer, bfd. M. Ferreira, Noticias Summarias das\n2. Perseguicoes da missa de Cochinchina, Lisboa, 1700, trg. 187-218. A. Launay, Histoire de la mission de Cochinchine, Ill, trg 510-520 ; JapSin 73,171.\n- (29) A. Launay, sdd, tr. 510\n- (30) Jap-Sin 73,171\n- (31) A. Launay, sdd, 520\n\nduoi su giao-huan cua mot danh-su do than-sinh ong lura chon Eén nam lén 25 tui, ong n?i tieng la mot nha nho thong-thai hoc-lurc vuot han cac ban dong mon va c6 thé cho phep 6ng. tr? nén mot quan-churc cao-trong. Luc bay gio ong da la mot thi-si thoi-danh.\n\nMot bien-c? xoay huong doi ong vao nim 1622, luic ong dugc 34 tubi : ong durgc doc cac sach giao-ly chir nho do cac cha Dong Tén ? Trung-hoa soan-thao. Ong ben nhap dao Thien-Chua va cha Manuel Fernandez thuoc Dong Tén da day dao va rira toi cho ong cung vg ong. Tir day ong tro hén mot giao-hiru cong-tac mat-thiet voi cac giao-si Dong Ten. Cha Manuel Fernandez da an-tru ? nba ong trong 6 thang de tranh con bat dao. Sau ong theo cha de lam thay-giang va nhieu ngiroi da tr? dao vi uy-tin, hoc-thirc, nhung loi giang-day va	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:591b677c6b5ce58c3827559d7443480d", "default:extract:d3075486370aab8e7c7ca4935d70f089"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:39
chunk-cd9e33304b2956cc92226297a680cd4e	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	109	800	(1) Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, Giao-si A Lich-Son Dac-Lo vbi. che quoc-ngu,\n\nVNKCIS s6 2 trang 105.\n\n(2) Thanh-lang, Nhing chang duong cia chi quoc-ngi, bdd trang 7.\n\nTrong chuong nay, chung ta se trinh bay phan dong gop cua nhung nguoi da -sang-che chtr quoc-ngir.\n\n## I. F.BUZOMI VA J. BALDINOTTI\n\n## (1625-1627)\n\nChung ta c6, the suy-luan ma khong xa sr that la cac giaosi truyén-giao tién-kh?i phai dung mot loi phien-am nhtrng nhan-danh dia-danh nuoc ta cung mot so ti-ngir cin-thiet. Trong nhung tai-lieu viet tay con luru-trv tai van-kh? Dong -u  uax au 9o nuo os nou dea ei sunuo 'eu-oa ? ua1 than chir quoc-ngi, ty-du nhu Thienchu (tirc Thien-chi) trong mot birc thur cua Francesco Buzomi viét nim 1925 hay 1926 (3) trong mot tac-pham cua J.Baldinotti in ? Ro-ma nam 1627\n\nchung ta thay tac-gia ghi mot vai chtr quoc-ngi hay Viet-ngt phien-am (4).\n\n## 11.— CHRISTOFORO BORRI (1631)\n\nChristoforo Borri la mot giao'si Dong Ten nguoi Y dén truyén-giao ? Dang Trong tr nam 16l8 dén nam 1921 Ciaosi c6 ghi chep mot s6 chtr quoc-ngi trong mot tac-pham xuatban ? Ro-ma nim 1631 nhan d la:\n\nRelatione della nuova missione delli P.P. Della Compagnia, di Giesu al Regno della Cocincina. Scrita dal Padre Christoforo Borri Milan\n\n(3) Xem Phon thur nhat, churong Il trang 111-112\n\n(4) J. Baldinotti, Relatione des Viaggio di Tunquin, trich trong Lettere\n\ndell'Ethiopia . . . Romae, 1629.\n\nese della medesina Compagnia, che fu uno de primi ch'entrono in delto Regno. Alla Santito di N. Sig. Urbano PP Ottavo. In roma\n\nPer Francesco Corbelliti MDCXXXI con licenza de Superiori.\n\nSau day la nhrng chir quoc-ngr do Christoforo Borri da ghi chép. Chung toi sao luc tir ban dich cua Bonifacy :\n\n- trang 285: Anam (An-nam) - trang 286: Lai (Lao) Cacciam (Ke Chiem = nguroi lang YhanhChiem, dia vuc Hoi-An xua Quamguya (Quang-nghia) Quignin (Qui-nhon) 1t trang 288: Renran (Da-rang, Ra-rang = Phu-yén) - trang 289: da den lut (da dn lut) · trang 292 : gnoo (nh?) 一 一 trang 30l : nayre (nai coi voi). - trang 306 : Nuocmon (Nuoc Man) trang 309 : doij (d6i) 1 1 (con nh? muon vao 1ong Hoa-lan chang) - trang 343 : onsaij (ong sai) — trang 350: muoecmam (nuoc mam) - trang 374: dan nura, da an het	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:4ff2316328be4c90c60edd26a052e38e", "default:extract:0b527cd67140932200ee1a2134e046ff"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:48
chunk-0744c2b188be605f069b0bbd958748f1	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	110	800	noo (nh?) 一 一 trang 30l : nayre (nai coi voi). - trang 306 : Nuocmon (Nuoc Man) trang 309 : doij (d6i) 1 1 (con nh? muon vao 1ong Hoa-lan chang) - trang 343 : onsaij (ong sai) — trang 350: muoecmam (nuoc mam) - trang 374: dan nura, da an het (da än nira, da an het) trang 382 : Tiu ciam bier (Tui chang biet) 1 - trang 383: on say di lay (ong sai di lai)\n\n- trang 386: Cakio (Thich-ca)\n- -- trang 388: Banco (Ban-co)\n- trang 389: maa (ma)\n- trang 394: maqui (ma quy) maco (ma co)\n- trang 396: Omgne (Ong nghe)\n- trang 399: Bua (Vua) Chiuua (Chua)\n- trang 401 : Kemoi (Ké Moi)\n\nD6 la nhung danh.tir, nhung tir-ngir va nhirng ciu ngan rai-rac trong tac-pham tiéng Y cia Christoforo Borri. Chung ta c6 thé xem d6 la tai-lieu in c6 nhat hien c6. Turong cuing nén luru y rang trong ban tiéng Y, nguoi ta khong phan-biet cht Y voi chtr quoc-ngir nén deu in mot kiéu cht. Trong ban tiéng Phap in  Lille, αnhirng chu Viet déu in nga (6) nhu trong ban tiéng Phap do Bonifacy dich.\n\nCan-cir vao nhtrng tai-lieu hiem-hoi trén day, chung ta c6 thé dua ra mot it nhan-xet ve le-l6i phien-am tieng Viet trong thoi-ky so-khai.\n\n- 1) Loi phien-am tien-khoi tieng Viet theo giong Y hay giong Bo ? D6 la mot de tai dugc Nguyen Khac-Xuyén va\n2. Thanh-Lang de-cap. Theo Nguyen Khac-Xuyén (7), Borri va\n\n(6) Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, Cong-cuoc khao-curu chir quoc-ngi vao nam 1931,\n\nVHNS Loai m6i, s6 42 théng 7 nm 1659, trang 689.\n\n(7) Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, bdd, trang 89.\n\n1a nguoi Y nén cau phien-am co khuynh-huong nga ve tiéng Y: nh dugc viét la gn (nhr quignin = Qui-nhon ; gnoo== nhd nh6); x dugc viet la sc (nhu scin = xin); ch dugc viet la c (nhr tuiciambiet = tui chang biet).\n\nThanh-Lang (8) trai lai, nhan-xét rang Borri, tuy la nguoi Y ma van phien-am theo l6i Bo va dan-chung: a chang han 18i phien-am nhung chi nhu Chiampa, chiu (chu) chia (tra) bia chiuua (vua-chua) ch