giao-si Alexandre de Rhodes den Dang Trong va giao-si c6 dip hoc-h?i Viet-ngu. Giao-si thu-nhan: α Vta toi mién Nam va nghe nguoi ban-xur n6i voi nhau, nhat la phu-nr, thi toi tu?ng nhr dugc nghe chim liu-lo h6t, dong thoi toi tu?ng khong bao gio c6 thé hoc\n\n(4) Xem Alexandre de Rhodes, Divers voyages et Missions... Lille 1854,\n\ntrang 29.\n\n(5) Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, Giao-si A-lich-son Dac-lo v6i chir quoc-ngi, bdd, trang 94.\n\ndugc thur tiéng d6》 (6). Nh	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:53f30dcf97c6097a456bc3736265a169", "default:extract:568f70b5e2a6cdc54aefbe88952f9eca"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:33:52
