in Litle Brittaine, 1633.\n\nsong ? Dang Trong 5 nam va thong-thao tieng Viet. Theo Cadiere (l8), duong nhu Borri cung biet tieng Viet kha nhieu dén do da dan nhieu tir-ngi Viet trong tac-pham nhung chua biét den mirc tinh-vi. That the, chinh Borri da thu nhan khi phu-nhan sir-than do Chua Dang Trong goi sang Cao-men yél ciu giao-si day dao cho Ba : α Toi - loi Cha Borri - xin l6i' khong the chap-thuan loi yeu-cau thanh-thien va huu-ly do ba da ng? voi toi boi vi mac dau c6 biet tieng Viet it nhieu, toi khong du tieng dé giang day han-hoi cho ba hieu biet miu-nhiem cao-ca ciia dao Chuia Kito》 (19).\n\nTheo tai-lieu Les Voyages et travaux des Missionnaires de la Compagnie de Jesus, giao-si Borri	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:c70f979ad7922a530316ba1501d5473f", "default:extract:b0434397af0537a657a97bf892ce36c3"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:34:12
