!l on enp 2p Aeu nx ? boi vi ? xir nay ma-quy khong gay nhieu tro-ngai'nhu ? Trung-hoa》. (4)\n\nNhung cha Pedro Alfaro .ban viec to-churc tu-vien ? AoMon nen khong.den truyén-giao ? nuoc ta nhu so-nguyen. Trong mot chuyen di sang Goa dé khieu-nai vé viec Cha von la nguoi Tay-ban-nha nen bi nguoi Bo truc-xuat khdi Ao-mons thuyén Cha gap bao va xac Cha troi-giat vao dät Chiem-thanh Cha dugc dan-chung dia-phuong hoa-tang (5).\n\n(3) Sdd, trang 30.\n\n(4) Conzalez	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:bf228f09fe0c272bc560f59b0131b12b", "default:extract:9e16b9bf5cf58e12fa60dab13617345a"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:34:17
