enade va phuc-vu trong quan-doi voi cap-buc -ny uo oayn yop-uenb oa lou gia-onn ngi oeq gueu 'n-aunn phong chirc.\n\nCha Ordonez de Cevallos dugc linh dua thi-hai mot gianImuc"nuoc Chili ve Tay-ban-nha, nlung thuyén bi bao dua giat vao bo bién Cuba. Tir La Havane, Cha tr? lai Me-tay-co roi' di qua Acapulo va Guayaquil de tr? ve Nouvelle-Grenade. Thang 10 nam 1589, Cha dap thuyén tir Guayaquil, gap bao nen thuyén troi vé phia Uc-dai-duong. Sau nhieu buoc giantruan, Cha cap ben Ao-mon ngay 1	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:810801de9b2b9f71d74e0ed83ad090e0", "default:extract:f3db91d1b1b9f69fabcae74ee511e04a"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:34:41
