cuon Tudié.t cia Durc cha Taberd xuat ban o Bengale (19) cia Louis Malleret, Vai diéu lien-quan den nhing 'tai-lieu chua xuät-ban ve cuon Tudin La-Viet cia Dirc cha Taberd in & Bengale (1836-1840) cia Karpales (20) Mot thi pham truong thien bang quoc-ngir co da dich ra Anh-ngir, Phap-ngi, La-ngi : Ine-tir-dqo van cia Phuong-	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:891ff0a44badf14155e6ad6009d3d446", "default:extract:2c315beeaa54c0938d98301824ba8680"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:29:35
chunk-c959098dc7368d059fe66c013c6ae462	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	11	800	phe-binh van-hoc va lich-sir van-hoc.\n\nLy-luan van-hoc c6 the xem la triet-hoc cua van-hoc, mucdich la trinh-bay ban-chat, ciru-canh cua tac-pham van-hoc. Phe-binh van-hoc la gioi anh-sang cua ly-luan van-hoc de tlm hieu tac-pham vé phrong-dien noi-dung va hinh-thirc, de xac.\n\ndinh gia-tri npi-tai cung nhu gia-tri lich-sir cia tac-pham van-\n\n(1) Xem tham : Pieire-Henri Simon, La Litterature du Peche et de la\n\nGrace, Artheme Fayard, Paris 1957 ; Jean Suberville, Théorie de I'Art et des Genres litteraires, Les éditions de IEcole, Paris, 1957; Nguyen van Trung, Luroc.khao Van-hoc, Nam-Son, Sai-gon, 1963. Tac-gia se thao-luan ky trong cuon Van-hoc nhap mon sap xuat-ban.\n\nhoc. Con lich-str van-hoc la cong-trinh xac-dinh vi-tri, gia-tri khuynh-huong cua tac-pham trong m?i tuong-quan voi tac-gia va thoi-dai tac-gia va trong khuon-kho tién-trien cua lich-sir. Ba mon nay lien-he mat-thiet voi nhau cung nhu lien-he dén nhieu khoa-hoc nhan-van khac. Nguoi ly-luan van-hoc tat nhién phai chap-nhan mot triet-hoc. Nguoi phe-binh van-hoc tat nhién phai phat-huy mot my-hoc. Nguoi viet lich-sir van-hoc tat nhien phai tham-kh?o nhtng phat-kien cua sur-hoc, chinh-tri- hoc, nhan-chung-hoc, phong-tuc-hoc v.v...\n\nTheo sy phan-tich trén day, van-hoc hieu qua nhing tacpham sang-tac la mot nghe-thuat, con van-hoc hieu qua nhirng cong-trinh ly-luan, phe-binh, lich-sir van-hoc la mot khoa-hoc Danh rang viét truyén, lam tho, viét kich la sang-tac, nhung bién-khao nghien-ciru ve cac sang-tac thuan-tuy ay c6 phai la sang-tac khong ? Thac-mac nay dat ra van-dé tinh-chat cua nhing sang-tac van-hoc thuan-tuy va tinh-chat cuia nhung congtrinh bien-khao nghien-ciru van-hoc. Ca hai dang déu la sangtac : van-hoc thuan-tuy la sir-dung ngon-ngir nghe-thuat, con bién-khao nghien-ciru van-hoc la sir-dung ngon-ngir cua khoahoc. Hoc-gia Pius Servien (2) c6 phan-biet ngon-ngir khoa-hoc ) - lu-uola toa (sous sp au) que), moi ngon-ngir c6 nhirng quy-luat va tac-dung rieng.\n\nTheo su phan-biet cua Pius Servien, chung ta c6 the n6i la bien-khao nghién-ciru van-hoc la sang-tic theo ngon-ngi\n\nkhoa-hoc, tuy cung sr-dung nhing ky-thuat irng-dung trong Sy sang-tac van-hoc nhung.nham muc-dich phat-huy chan-ly trong cai van-pham; con sang-tac van-hoc thuan-tuy la sangtac theo ngon	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:3c15a0086be21aad4a89c54f80d1305e", "default:extract:e58bcc9f2c8285cff4eb2c3e441a80ce"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:29:42
chunk-6f1f28ad8a3e7ba5d729118cd3272aab	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	20	800	ong thiet-yéu lien-he voi mot nén van-hoa nao. La su can-thiep cua Tinh Yéu Thién-Chia cac nén van-hoa de dan dua cac dan-toc tr? vé vbi ThienChua. Nguoi ta ngo-nhan khi dong-h6a dao Cong-giao v6i bat cir nen van-h6a nao (2).\n\n(2) Xem them : Jean Danielou, Essai sur le mystere de Ihistoire, Editions du Seuil, Paris.\n\noep oaun yonau wax f-og go 5p ey longu 'e uguu-oau oa Cong-giao nhu la ke da dirng ra ngoai 1e truyén-thong van-h6a dan-toc.\n\nSur that thi dao Cong-giao th6ng-nhat nhan-loai trong diurc tin nhung khong dong-nhat cac dan-toc theo mot van-h6a nao. Truyén-thong dan-toc, dac-diem van-h6a, néu khong c6 gi lam sai-lac hoac tr? ngai sir-diep Tinh Yeu Thien-Chua, deu dugc bao-ton va phat-trien trong khuon-kho dao Cong-giao. Xét vé mat xa-hoi, durc tin Cong-giao chinh la mot sirc manh boiduong cho 1ong ái-quoc cang them virng ben.\n\nDao Cong-giao thong nhat nhan-loai trong durc-tin, nhung d6 la mot su thong-nhat ton-trong moi sr di-biet tat-nhien gitra cac dan-toc. Moi dan-toc c6 mot lich-sir, mot hoan-canh sinh-hoat rieng biet, do d6 c6 ca-tinh doc-dao, truong-ton voi voi van-menh quoc-gia va cau-tao nén quoc-hon qu?c-tuy. Cac dan-toc Tay-phuong trai qua bao the-ky chiu anh-hu?ng Cong giao van bao-ton durgc ve dac-sac co-hru. Truong-hop cac dan-toc A, Phi dugc truyén-giao trong thoi-gian gan day cung the. Cac gia-tri tich-cuc cua A, Phi cung tuon tran ve Daiauonyd-e yoew-uonau sunqu el nyu oia-auo Suonp\n\nNhung nhan-dinh khai-quat tren day dugc chirng-nghiem . trong cong cuoc truyén-ba dao Cong-giao ? Viet-Nam : chung ta nhan thay dirc tin Cong-giao dugc phat-huy ma tinh-chat dan-toc van dugc ton-trong.\n\nVan-hoc Cong-giao Viet-Nam bieu-lo y-huong phat-huy tinh-than dan-toc. Tha-thiet voi van-menh to-quoc, tran-trong bao-ton va phat-trien cac gia-tri van-h6a cua dan-toc, d6 la nhrng y-lyc huong-dan cong-trinh sang-tac va bién-khao cua cac the-he nha van Cong-giao Viet-Nam.\n\nTrong the-he tien-phong, cac giao-si truyen.giao ngoaiqu6c va bon-quoc da n6i len long kinh-mén dan Viet dur6i troi Nam. Loi tam·sy cua Alexandre de Rhodes c6 the xem la noi long cua cac giao-si truyen-giao ngoai-quoc :\n\nα Toi tir gia xir Nam bang the-xac nhung chang phai bang long tri, ca doi voi xur Bic cing vay, that sur tam-hon toi de tron o hai noi ay va toi tuong khong bao	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:a50f22188ec377a1cf8cc1f7f83f028b", "default:extract:849741c40d7fd290c72dac2d6799fc10"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:29:46
chunk-b9789584353c983df2a427d66c75df75	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	25	800	voi quan-niem so-menh, Phatgiao voi quan-niem nghiep-qua va Cong-giao voi quan-niem nhan-ai la α nhtrng cai vi-dai v, da di sau vao doi song tinh-than cua dan-toc :α Thyc la mot cai may-min la-lung het sirc khi ca ba nén ton-giao voi ba y-niem vi-dai ay duong nhao-nan tinh-than nguoi Viet-Nam tren dat nuoc Viet-Nam v (8).\n\nTi loi dung ngr hanh van den cach ty-tinh dat y, vanhoc Viet-Nam da thira-nhan nhtng gia-tri C6ng-giao nhu la nhtrng gia-tri nhan-ban pho-bien.\n\nLong kinh mén Durc Me da durgc dien-ta bang nhung bai 'donn fy-ayn naiyu ni uep-ogia guon Sunn-uaAnyi poy Bupp upa o unu-u ea nin-u in-ga g kg ua ieq unun mot dia-vi kha-quan trong kho tang van-hoc binh-dan. Toi dan-cir mot bai do Chuong-Thi suu-tam duoi nhan- de αTien hoan:\n\nChing con ddng tim long thanh, May loi van phuic, may nganh Man-Coi. Kinh dang hoa trang khoe turoi, Ngoi khen Dirc Me. tron doi dong-trinh. Kinh dang hoa tim ve xinh, Chi Me ep xac ham minh lap cong. Chuing con ddng doa hoa hong. Ngoi khen Dirc Me virng long kinh tin. Lai xin dang doa hoa vang. Kinh Me chiu kho can trang virng gan. Kinh dang doi doa hoa xanh, Vi nhur phuc-dirc duom nhuan Me nay.\n\n- (8) Le van Sieu, Nhing cai vi-dai, in trong Nien-lich van-chuong Tinh-Viet Sai-gon 1959. Xem them : Nhung gi6-tri nhan-ban trong truyen-thong turtrong Viet-Nam cue Thu-nhan trong Von-hoa nguyet-san, thang 7,1965:\n\nSai-gon, trang 1077-1089.\n\nHop nhau nam sac mot nganh,\n\nTo long kinh men Me lanh lien lien (9).\n\nNam sac hoa kia voi hurong thom nong ngat durc tin Cong-giao da lam cho vuon hoa van-hoc binh-dan them ngatngao ryc-ro. Nguoi yéu-mén van-hoc binh-dan khong the khong tran-trong nam sic hoa cua mot nguon cam-hirng moi, cung nhu da tirng bui ngui thuong-tiec khi nhin α nu tam xuan n? ra xanh biec 》 hoac tran-ngap my-cam khi nhan thay αhoa 'α Huep nip nel woyi lonq eoy sugq suouy ngau eoy fl eou iel Tir mau xanh biec cua tinh vo-vong, huong bu?i cua quehurong than-men den sac hoa kinh dang Durc Me Dong-Trinh, nguoi binh-dan Viet-Nam da thoi vao the.dieu luc-bat co. kinh cua nen van-hoc binh-dan mot luong sinh-khi sieu-nhien. Tinh-chat pho-bien cua dirc tin Cong-giao da di sau vao thanh-am tir-dieu cia dan-toc.\n\nD6 la mot hanh-trinh khong phai mot som mot chieu ma thanh-tuu. Trong thoi-ky so-khai dao Cong-giao ? VietNam, cac nha tho da gap nhieu noi kh	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:26118c87779f816a72e638ad4f45b5f7", "default:extract:d90eea2ab444cd9dc7904c291c467e8f"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:29:50
chunk-0a0f3cae85122e8c444f4aa22f909e1b	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	23	800	-do. Cai 16i chur riéng ay, sau do hai nha truyén-giao-sur nguoi Bo-dao-nha, roi sau den c6 A-lich son Dac.lo nguoi Phap to-churc lai thanh mot thir chtr thong-dung chung trong truyen-giao hoi, tirc la thuyto cua chtr quoc-ngir ngay nay v. (5)\n\nDe cap dén Huinh-tinh Cua va Trurong-vinh Ky, hai nha van Cong-giao dugc ke Ia nhirng nha van α tién phong 》 cua nen van-hoc cht quoc-ngir, cac hoc-gia khong tiec loi tan-duong.\n\nVe Huinh-tinh Cua, nha ngir-hoc Le ngoc Tru de-cao'cong nghiep soan bo tu-dien dau·tien bang tieng Viet:\n\nα Bac tien phong mien Nam c6 chi huong thi c6 Huinhtinh Pualus Cua tinh-thong Han-hoc va Phap-ngir. ngoai viec viét bao, viét sach, da soan bo tu-vi truoc tien bang tieng Viet, bo Dai-nam quac-am tyr-vj thau-tap va giai-thich nhtng tieng, nhing tir-ngir duong thoi, durng dugc co-ban cho nen hocthuat van-h6a nuéc nha (6).\n\nVé Trrong-vinh Ky, nha phe-binh Le Thanh cong nhan la α byc nguyen-huan cua cai thoi -dai van-chuong mbi m. α Ngay nay ... ta nhan ? Truong tien - sinh hai muc.dich : dem ra anh sang cai di-san van-hoc cua ta, truoc dé gir lay\n\n(5) Viet-Nam van-hoa sir cuong, trang 270.\n\n(6) Chur qu8c-ngu tir the-ky XVll den cubi the-ky tho XiX, in trong Viet-\n\nNam khao co tap san so 2, trang 134.\n\n6 trong cai hinh-tugng trong-treo cia n6, sau de lam khuong cho nguoi sau, pho-thong chi nuoc nha, dem n6 lam phuong tien truyén-ba tur-tuong va hy-vong mot ngay kia n6 se thanh (u?c-van cua ta, kh?i phai cai toi di hoc nho nhu truoc. ) (7)\n\nBay nhieu doan vien-dan tuy chua day-du vé nhing nhan-vat va giai-doan hinh-thanh cht quoc-ngir, nhung cing du chirng-minh rang nhtrng tac-pham cua nguoi Cong-giao Viet-Nam, ngoai gia-tri hien-nhien ve ton-giao, c6 mot dia-vi quan trong lich-sir van-hoc dan-toc.\n\nC6 the n6i syr hinh -thanh chu quoc-ngr xac-nhan ring cong-trinh van-hoc cua nguoi Cong-giao dap-irng mot nhu-cau thiet-yéu cua dan-toc Viet-Nam.\n\nNhirng ky-vong ma tien-nhan da dat cong-trinh sang-che chir nom, ngay nay toan dan da thay dan-da thyc-hien trong cht quoc-ngir. Tieng Viet phien-am bang mau-ty la-tinh da tiép-tuc mot cach hoan-hao sur-mang cua chtr nom trong cong cuoc xay-dung mot nen quoc-hoc. Trong qua trinh lich-str, cac Ky-to-htru voi cong-cuoc van-dong hinh-thanh chtr quoc-ngu, di tiep-t	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:a572800c35f48197fa3a50d32d5897bb", "default:extract:5819bbbd04ac986304aabedb295aa3e8"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:29:54
chunk-72520beb7bd0f32f4977e2747321455f	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	56	800	mien la khong cong-khai trainghich dao Cong-giao va thuan-phong my-tuc ", b?i vi α dirc Suoud ea tuau-ai sunqu yu-iinu wen Aey yonp enx suouy tuc, mien la khong phai la x?u-xa va trai lai durc.tin chu-truong la dang dugc ton-trong》 (40).\n\nKhi cac tan giam-muc va thira-sai thuoc Hoi Ngoai-quoc Truyén-giao Ba-le den dat Viet, lich-sir truyén-giao va van-hoc cong-giao buroc sang mot giai-doan khac nhr se de - cap dén trong cuon II cua bo sach nay.\n\n*\n\n*米\n\nChung ta da trinh-bay tinh-hinh chinh-tri, van-hoc va truyén-giao trong khoang thoi-gian phat-sinh van-hoc conggiao Viet-Nam. Dao Cong-giao du-nhap Viet-Nam trong mot thoi-ky khung-hoang phat-trién. Xa-hoi Viet-Nam trong théky XVI va tien ban the-ky XVII la mot xa-hoi dang bienchuyen theo nhirng duong-huong moi. Trong boi-canh lichsr ay, dirc tin Cong-giao da nay mam va sinh-dong, tao nén Giao-hoi Cong-giao Viet-Nam. Nen-tang tinh-than thay doi thi thé-cach dien-dat tinh-ty, cam-nghi cuing thay d?i theo. D6 1a nguyen-nhan xau-xa cua nén van-hoc Cong-Giao Viet-Nam.\n\n(39) nhur tren, trang\\_ 149. Chi-thi cua Bo Truyén-giao ngay 10-11-1959 goi\n\ncho Duc Cha Pallu.\n\n(40) nhur tren, trang 150. Tai-lieu da dan.\n\n## CHUCNG II\n\n## SU HINH-THANH NGON-NGU' CONG-GIAO\n\nta phai xét sy hinh-thanh cua ngon-ngir Cong-giao VietNam truoc khi di sau vao cac van-pham Cong-giao cht nom va chir quoc-ngir.\n\nSu6t the-ky XVI, khong c6 sr-lieu nao churng-to cac thia-sai Cong-giao thong-thao Viet-ngu. Le. di nhien, muon truyén-giao trong thoi-ky nay cin phai c6 thong-ngon. Chung. ta co thé phong-doan ho la nhtng thuong-gia ngoai-quoc vl nhu-cau thuc-te phai tap n6i tieng Viet de giao-thiep voi ngir trong gibi than-can cac thuong-gia ngoai-quoc.\n\nTrong tien-ban the-ky XVIl, c6 nhieu Cha Dong Tén si hay tu-si Phat-giao. Le di-nhien, trinh-do Viet-ngr cing hoc-h?i Viet-ngur, c6 nhieu giao-hiru tinh-turong chr Han va chr Nom. Trong s6 nhirng giao-hiru tan-tong, c6 nguoi la nhonhu trinh-do giao-ly cuia ho tién-bo hon nhtng lop nguoi\n\nthong-ngon trong the-ky truoc. Do d6 sy chuyen-dich danh-tir Cong-giao tir ngon-ngir Tay-phuong sang Viet-ngir c6 phan my-man hon. Tir sy chuyén-dich la giai-phap cap-thoi, giaosi va giao-dan lai no-lurc sang-che cac danh-tir Cong-giao dung voi tin-ly va thich-urng v	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:4eee0fe75b91f0204dbf1606fc040f7d", "default:extract:39117e390ed838a3b189664789f4788a"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:58
