n tan noi dieu-tra thi thay nhu sau : Mot anh phuong cheo mac áo gia lam nguoi Bo-dao-nha. Y goi dira bé lai ben, hoi xem n6 c6 muon di theo dao m6i hay khong. Khi dira beé t? y bang long, y vach ao bung ra, dau dira bé vao trong. Ti d6, cai nguoi Bo-dao-nha tra hinh mang cai bung'ba chira to ghe-gom, miéng n6i ba-hoa, khong con thiéu tro he gi. Gitra luc khan-gia ho thet curoi reo, thi y vach ao ran de ra mot dira bé, roi y bao n6 : α Tr	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:4bdbd0f36d201172c94dea9ebcb4e389", "default:extract:b8cc9a8ee21552fbb21617ec31852542"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:03
chunk-017d16f20e81b88f579558eb1de96381	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	52	800	moi lén duong di Auchau de van-dong thanh-lap hang giao-pham & Viet-Nam.\n\nTinh cho den nam 1964 la nam Cha Louis Chevreuil thuoc Hoi Truyén-giao Ngoai-quoc Ba-le dén Dang Trong, con c6 nhieu Cha Dong Ten dén truyén-giao nhur cac Cha Metello Saccano, Baldassare Cadeira, Fransesco Rivas, Dominique Fuciti, Pierre Marquez, Ignace Baudet.\n\nGiao-hoi Dang Trong phat trien manh-me, nhtng giao-huu dao-durc, sot-sang dugc giao-si ghi nhan la ba Gioanna, mot ba quy-phai tai Ke Cham dugc Cha Buzomi rira toi nam 1616, ba Minh-Dirc Vuong-thai dugc Cha Pina rira toi nam (l626) (32), ba Maria Manuéle.. Cac thay giang da cong-sy chat-che\n\n- (31) Christoforo Borri, Relatione della nuova missione delli P.P. Della Compa-\n2. gnia di Giesu al Regno della Cocincina Scrita dal Padre Christoforo Borri Milan ex della medisina Compagnia, che fu uno de primi ch'entrono in delto Regno. Roma 1731, co ban dich tiéng Phap, Anh, Hoa-lan, Dirc, va La-tinh..\n- (32) Xem Pham dinh Khieme Minh Duc Vuong Thai-Phi, Tinh Viet van doan\n4. Saigon,1957.\n\nvoi cac Cha va thay the cac Cha nhirng luc cac Cha phai an- tranh hay bi truc-xuat. Trong s6 nhtrng vi tong-do giao-dan nay, ta phai ké thay giang An-re Phu-yen, tur-dao tién-khoi giao-hoi Dang trong nam 1644 (33), cac thay giang Y-nha-xu Quang-tri va Vinh-Son Quang-ngai nam 1645.\n\n## b) 37 nam truyén-giao & Dang Ngoai (1626-1663)\n\nNoi den viec truyén-giao o Dang Ngoai la phai n6i den Alexandre de Rhodes truoc tién, mac dau Cha khong phai la linh-muc Dong Ten dau-tien den Dang Ngoai.\n\nNam 1626, Giuliano Baldinotti dén Dang Ngoai voi mot thay trg-si nguoi Nhat Giulio Piani dé khao-sat trién-vong truyen-giao. Tiep theo phuc-trinh cua Cha Giuliano Baldinotti, cac Cha Alexandre de Rhodes va Pierre Marquez dugc dieu-dong tir Dang Trong ra Dang Ngoai de lo viéc truyén-giao.\n\nHai Cha dén Cira Bang (Thanh-h6a) ngay 19-3-1627 nham le Thanh Giu-se nén chon Thanh Giu-se lam bon-mang Dang Ngoai. Su lra chon ay se dugc cac dirc giam-muc ban quyén chap-thuan. Hai thang sau Cha rira toi dugc 200 nguroi (34).\n\nChua Trinh Trang c6 nha-y tang cac Cha mot ngoi nha bang go, mot phan nh6 dé ?, mot phan lon lam nha tho. Dén\n\n- (33) Xem Pham dinh Khiem, Nguoi ching thur nhat, Tinh Viet van doan, Sai-. gon,1959.\n\n(34) Xem C.A. Poncet, le voyage du Pere A. de Rhodes de Cira Bang a Ha\n\nnoi en 1627 in trong BAVH,	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:c345e55dc46d3d5628b126acc5b73384", "default:extract:5d647783d3b4b4df826cf700df3d40f9"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:04
chunk-1c4f3f8c7da107161d259614fd44cee2	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	62	800	dira beé t? y bang long, y vach ao bung ra, dau dira bé vao trong. Ti d6, cai nguoi Bo-dao-nha tra hinh mang cai bung'ba chira to ghe-gom, miéng n6i ba-hoa, khong con thiéu tro he gi. Gitra luc khan-gia ho thet curoi reo, thi y vach ao ran de ra mot dira bé, roi y bao n6 : α Tr nay may la dura c6 dao n. Giao-si Buzomi hiéu ngay day chi la mot tro he c6 y che-gieu cach day dao ngo-ngin cua cac nha truyen-giao di truoc ong. Cach hoi nguoi theo dao chi la hoi xem ho c6 muon tr? nen nguoi Bodao-nha hay khong. Theo dao moi chi la thay-di quoc-tich chir khong phai thay-doi ton-giao ) (8).\n\nHai doan van trén day, ngoai cong-dung cho biet nhing nguoi theo dao Cong-giao da bi che-gieu den do tr? nén· de-tai cho mot hai-kich, con churng-t6 rang nhung nguoi thong-ngon chua hieu yéu-tinh cua dao Cong-giao. Cau h?i ngo-ngan cia\n\n(8) Bartoli, Historia della Compagnia di Gesu, La Cina 3a Parte dell Asia; Roma 1663 trang 616. Thanh-Lang trich-dich trong Bieu nhat lam van-\n\nhoc can-dai, tap 1. Tu-Do xuat-ban, Sai-gon 1958, trang 19-20.\n\nlio c6 the khien cho nhung nguoi ngoai dao Cong-giao hieu lim rang theo dao. Cong-giao Ia thay doi quoc-tich.\n\nCung nhu danh-xung Hoa-lang dqo, 'ngon-ngr cua nhurng nguoi thong-ngon chirng-t? rang dao Cong-giao chua dugc chuyen-dich voi nhirng danh-tir dat-y.\n\nIHI. SU DONG GOP CUA GIAO-SI\n\nFRANCESCO BUZOMI (1615-1622)\n\nSy hinh-thanh cua ngon-ngr Cong-giao buoc sang mot cesco Buzomi, Be Tren. phai-doan truyen-giao Dang Trong.\n\nNhu da noi ? doan trén, tan hai-kich che-gieu nguoi theo dao Cong-giao dien ra nam I6l5, luc giao-si Buzomi moi dat chan dén Dang Trong. Giao-si nhan thay cau hoi cua nguoi thong-ngon lap lai trong hai-kich la ngo-ngan sai-lam nen da thay doi thanh mot cau c6 y-nghia hon: Muon bau dau Christiam chiam ? (phien-dien theo chinh-ta ngay nay la : Muon vao dao Christiam chang ?) (9).\n\nTrong but-tich cua giao-si Francesco Buzomi, chac c6 nhirng di-tich ngon-ngir Cong-giao do giao-si hiéu-chinh hay sang-che. Theo su khao-ciru cua linh-muc Nguyen Khac-Xuyén (10), trong mot van-kien de ngay 20-5-l622 tai Nuoc Man\n\n(9) Xem Thanh-lang, sdd, trang 19\n\n(10) Nguyen Khac Xuyen, Chung quanh van-de thanh-lap chir quoc-ngi vao nam 1645, VHNS loai m6i, s6 48 théng 1-2 nam 1960 trang 2.\n\nuoa -oa i on n un (o-) Ro-ma du6i ky hieu ARSI Jap.	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:2ea0ab7135e907d9117f7700a8f9a6d5", "default:extract:d564f37bfda77ba1f8f90fafddae0ec0"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:10
chunk-aec033da7dbad9f2ff9c8d0b56d1edf9	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	34	800	xa-hoi Viet-Nam tir the-ky XVI. Ching ta cho rang vain-hoc Congsoy-upa pnb-noy yuow upyu ap p1 IAX (y-ayi ni ngp ipq opia\n\ntat nhien cia cong-cuoc truyén-giao. That ra, trong thé-ky XVI, cong-cupc truyen-giáo chura dugc to-chirc qui-mo va cung nhur chura co tac-pham van-hoc dang ke. Ke tir the-ky XVII tro di, nen van-hoc Cong-giao moi chinh-thirc phat-sinh trong khuon-kho cong cujc truyén-giao do cac Cha Dong Ten phu-trach tir nam 1615 Dang Trong va tir nam 1626 o Dang Ngoai.\n\nThoi-ky thir nhat cia van-hoc Cong-giio Viet-Nam chim dirt vao giira the-ky XVII. Gioi-han ndy can-cir vao nhing bien-co quan-trong ve lich-sir va van-hoc.\n\nDo sur van-dong cua gido-si Alexandre de Rhodes, nam 1658, Durc Giao-Hoang Alexandre VII bo-nhiem cac giam-muc tien-khoi o Viet-Nam.\n\nKé tir diy, cong-cuoc truyén-giao buoc sang mot giai-doan moi va nen van-hoc Cong-giao Viet-Nam cing bien-tinh.\n\nDang khac, nhirng vi'co cong voi nen van-hoc Cong-giao trong giai-doan dau tien cung tir tran vdo giira the-ky XVII : Alexandre de Rhodes mat nim 1660, Girolamo Majorica nam 1656, Gioan Thanh-Minh nam 1663.\n\nThoi-ky thir nhat cia van-hoc Cong-giao Viet-Nam manh-nha trong the-ky XVI, hinh-thanh trong tien-ban the-ky XVII se dugc nghien-ciru trong cac churong sau day :\n\nChuong I  : Bi-canh lich sir.\n\nChurong II  : Sur hinh-thanh ngon-ngir Cong-giao.\n\nChuong III  :  Van-hoc Cong-giao truyen-khau.\n\nChuong IV : I\n\nNhiung cong-trinh van-hoc Cong-giao Nhat- Ban va Trung-Hoa quan-he voi van-hoc Cong-giao Viet-Nam.\n\nChuong V  : Van-hoc Cong-giao chir nom.\n\nChuong\n\nVI  : Cong-cuoc sang-che chir quoc-ngir.\n\nChuong\n\nVII : Vin-hoc Cong-giao chir quoc-ngir.\n\nChuong\n\nVIII : Van-hoc Cong-giao chir quoc-ngir (tiép theo).\n\nIX : Tic-pham quoc-sir va giao-sir ngoqi-ngir.\n\nhurong moi.\n\n## CHUONG 1 BO1.CANH LICH.SU\n\nEN van-hoc Cong-giao phat-sinh trong mot thoi-ky c6 nhieu bien-co trong-dai. C6 the n6i rang the-ky XVI va tien-ban the-ky XVI1 la mot thoi-ky khung-hoang tram-trong. bao-hieu sy truong-thanh cua dan-toc theo nhurng duong\n\n## I.- TINH-HINH CHINH-TRI\n\nSu tan-ra nén thong-nhat hanh-chanh va viec m?-mang bo-coi vé phia Nam la nhrng bién-co lam thay-doi sinh-hoat va cac co-cau quoc-gia.\n\n## 1. Nha Mac cuop ngoi nha Lé.\n\nThe-ky XVI bat dau voi su suy-tan cia nha Hau-Le (1428-1527	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:ff2e1a705917d105ccc9b750b17f15aa", "default:extract:18bf1665747e96ec2588e7f812d19e81"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:30:04
chunk-3076219038266f5c4b3d12c15523358d	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	55	800	de van-dong viec bo-nhiem cac Dirc Giam-muc. Cha tuong-trinn voi Bo Truyén-Giao va Dirc Giao-Hoang vé giao-hoi Viet-Nam: uoc ching c6 300.000 giao-huru, hang nam c6 the tang thém 15.000 linh-hon, .can phai c6 300 linh- muc de coi-s6c (37). Cha de-nghi xin Dirc Thanh Cha trach-\n\n(37) Xem Lhapoulie, Rome et les missions d'lndochine.\n\ncir cac Dirc Giam-muc sang Viet-Nam de dao-tao cac giao-si ban-quoc, lua-chon trong so cac thay-giang α hien dang tu-dirc nhu trong bic Linh-muc n.\n\nLuc bay gio. theo cac sac-du cua cac Durc Giao-Hoang Léon X (1514-1516), Paul I11 (1539), Pau1 IV (1553) Grégoire: XIII (1573), Paul V (l6l6), chinh-phu Bo-dao-nha α bao-tro ) viec truyen-giao ? Vien-Dong. De tranh suy xung-dot, cha A-. lexandre de Rhodes de-nghi cac vi Giam-muc sang Viet-Nam se do Toa-thanh ban tuoc-hieu Dai-Dien Tong-Toa (vicaire apostolique) tai cac dan ngoai (in partibus infidelium), chr khong: mang tuoc-hieu Giam-Muc Chinh-Toa (éveque résidentiel).\n\nHoi Truyén-giao Ngoai-quoc Ba-le durgc thanh-lap dé cungcap Linh-muc thira-sai. Ngay 29-7-1658, Dirc Giao-Hoang Alexandre Vll, cir cha Francois Pallu lam Giam-muc hieu-toa.\n\nHéliopolis coi-s6c Giao-hoi Dang Ngoai, Cha Lambert de la Motte. lam Giam-muc hieu-tda Beryte coi-s6c Giao-hoi Dang Trong..\n\nNhiem-vu cap-bach cua cac Dirc tan Giam-muc la α truyén: cac chirc thanh ke ca chirc Linh-muc n va tuy-nghi cho doc kinh.\n\nbang ngon-ngr ban-quc》 (38)\n\nTheo truyén-thong khon-ngoan cua Giao-hoi, Toa Thanh La-ma can-dan cac Giam-muc α tranh xa viec chinh-tri > boi vl α xen-lan vao chinh-tri thi thiet-thoi cho ton-giao va lam cho.\n\n38) Archives MEP. Vol 247. Trich-dich theo Nguyen Hou-Trong, les Origines du clerge vietnamien, Tinh. Viet Sai-gon, 1957, trang 47-48.\n\ncac thura-sai xao-nhang muc-vu, mac dau xen-lan thi thay co them hy-vong chac se phat.trién ton-giao va truyén-ba dirc tin 》(39).\n\nVe van-de thich-nghi van-h6a, Toa Thanh chi-thi ton-trong van-h6a phong-tuc dia-phuong α mien la khong cong-khai trainghich dao Cong-giao va thuan-phong my-tuc ", b?i vi α dirc Suoud ea tuau-ai sunqu yu-iinu wen Aey yonp enx suouy tuc, mien la khong phai la x?u-xa va trai lai durc.tin chu-truong la dang dugc ton-trong》 (40).\n\nKhi cac tan giam-muc va thira-sai thu	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:d3163573a25483393c2280a492fb8ba8", "default:extract:0e7eb48a42bff53295241229731cf21c"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:16
chunk-2dace3ea8e4d0143cc03e62cb9b66d86	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	68	800	Can-cir vao nhirng bao-cao vé tin-tirc nhan dugc tir VietNam, cha Mathias de Maya, quan-nhiem Dong Tén tinh-hat Nhat-ban soan-thao vao nam 1649 mot ban bao-cao day 45 trang lan voi thu-cap thay-giang An-re Phu-yen. Theo van-lieu nay, Thay-giang An-re da tir-gia cac giao-hiru lan sau het vao nam 1644 nhur sau : α... Ju nghiao cui duc choe Jesu cho den est eoj cho den blen doij".\n\nPhién-dien theo chinh-ta ngay nay va them cho tron cau, ta c6 :\n\n(αHoi anh em, chung ta hay) gir nghia cung Dirc Chua Gie-su cho den het hoi, cho den tron doi v.\n\nGiao-si Alexandre de Rhodes c6 thuat lai cau nay, dich tir Phap-van ra nhur sau :\n\nα Hoi anh em, ta hay trung-tin cing Dirc Chua Troi cho dén chet ; khong mot dieu gi co the giap tat long kinh-men Chua Gie-su\n\nKi-to trong trai tim tav (18).\n\nVa theo Ioi tuong thuat cua giao-si Rlexandre de Rhodes, thay-giang An-re da khong ngot doc ten cuc trong : Giesu 1 Maria ! khi dao-phi dam mui giao vao khoang giua hai ba vai, xuyén sau lung ra tru?c ngurc.\n\n(18) Alexandre de Rhodes, La glorieuse mort.. trang 53. Pham Dinh-Khiem\n\ntrich-djch, sdd trang 154.\n\nMot dieu la-lung da xay ra khi dau thay.giang da roi kh?i cuong hong. Chung ta hay nhuong loi cho giao-si Alexandre de Rhodes :\n\nα Nguoi thanh nién thanh-thien nay (nhu tren da n6i) van khong ngot doc thanh-danh Chuia Giesu; ngay luc dau thay nay da roi khoi cuong hong va nam nga trén vai ben phai, toi nghe thay ro-rang tén curc-trong Gie-su ay phat ra tir vét thuong noi c°, cung mot giong giong het nhu tir cira mieng phat ra luc truoc ; toi nghe thay the r?-rang va tat ca nhirng nguoi gan toi luc ay deu n6i nhu vay, vira vui-ming lai vira kinh-ngac 》(19).\n\nCau n6i do Cha Mathias de Maya nhac lai va cac thanhdanh do cha Alexandre de Rhodes ghi chep la tai-lieu de chung ta nhan-dinh ve ngon-ngr cong-giao cua thay-giang An-re cuing nhur cua nhung giao-heu duong-thoi.\n\nthuy, chirng-t? rang dao Cong-giao da nhap-the trong tiéng Viet.\n\nCac danh-tir phien-am Gie-su, Ma-ri-a, qua l6i phat-am thong-thiet cam-dong cua thay-giang An-re trong mot trronghop tir-dao vinh-quang, da dugc rira roi de nhap-tich he-thong thanh-van Viet-ngur bang gia mau va tr? nén thong-dung.\n\nDi-ngon cua mot nguoi da song dao nhu thay giang Anré chirng to rang tieng Viet da bat dau c6 kha-nang dien-dat mot Dao Song.\n\n## VI1.- CONG-THUC RU'A TO1 (1645)\n\nNam 1645, theo de-nghi cuia giao-si Alexandre de Rhodes, 35 giao-si Dong Tén truyen-giao tai Viet-Nam, Trung	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:82e956e81c72f72dcfa2bd2f08aaea01", "default:extract:371a86b2dee02b6eb6581c3bb8b3146f"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:24
chunk-a20c35ede3cabc7d6019b8284db54bb4	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	70	800	Cuoc thao-luan rat soi-noi ve tir-ngir nhan danh va cac quan-diem dugc phat-bieu la tai-lieu giup chung ta hiéu-biet v tinh-hinh ngon-ngr Cong-giao luc bay gio.\n\nDao Cong-giao tin rang chi c6 mot Thien-Chua nhung imot Thien-Chua Ba Ngoi. Dieu quan-he la phai n6i the nao dé hiéu ro la mot Thien-Chua ba ngoi-vi, chur khong phai la ba\n\nThien-Chua.\n\nNhung y-kien d6i-lap dugc néu ra trong cuoc thao-luan lién-he den tir-ngir nhan danh.\n\nC6 nguoi muon dung tieng Viet thuan-tuy thay vi tiéng\n\n(22) Xem P.MD'Elia. De prima forme baptisimatis apud Sinenses signis sinensibus expressa, trong Péridioca, trang 2 Roma 1938 trang 340-348.\n\nChu-thich cua Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, bdd trang 4.\n\nHan-Viet va cong-thirc la : Tau lay ten Cha vd con va Spirito\n\nSanto tau rira mdy.\n\nPhii chu-truong dung nhan danh vien-ly rang nhan danh da gon va dep hon tau liy ten lai da dugc cong-nhan ? Trung Hoa nen c6 th' dung ? Viet-Nam.\n\nNhung nguoi ta ho-nghi vé s6 it hay s? nhieu cua chi danh nen c6 nhieu giai-phap da néu ra.\n\nGiai-phap cia nhtrng nguoi ho-nghi do-dy la dung tieng La-tinh voi cong-thirc : In nomine Cha va Con va Spirito Santo hay dung ting Bo-dao-nha voi cong-thirc : In nome Cha vd Con vd Spirito Santo. Cong-thirc Bo-dao-nha da bi che-gieu vi in nome da bi nhai la in u me voi y-nghia u-me trong tieng Viet.\n\nBuan ei uuu u yip uonu yonau gunuu eno deud-i Viet cuing khac-biet nhau tir quan diem cua ho ve s6 it hay so nhieu ciia chir danh.\n\nGiao-si Alexandre de Rhodes thuoc nhom thieu-s? khong cong-nhan tir-ngir nhan danh va chu-truong dung nhan nhat danh vi so rang danh co nghia la nhieu danh, nhieu ten. Trong ty-dién Viet-Bo-La, giao-si cuing ho-nghi nhu the : α Nhin danh Cha (Nhan danh Cha) : In nomine Patris est dubium an habeat eum sensum nghia la Nhan danh Cha : ho-nghi khong biet co phai nghia áy khong ".\n\nMot so giao-dan khong dong quan-diem vbi giao-si Alexandre de' Rhodes. Cha Thanh-Lang c6 phat-giac bien-ban\n\nla trang chi Nom, bén canh chu Nom có ghi-chu chur Quocngir va chtr La-tinh, nguyén-van phien-dien nhu sau :\n\nα Nhin danh Cha va Con va Phirito Sangtoi nai Annam cac bon dao thi tin rang ra ba danh bi bang muon i lam mot thi phay n6y nhin nhit danh Cha ecc... toy la. Giu ao cai (?) Tram (?) cu nghi bai toy la An.re Sen (?) cu nghi bai toy la Ben to uan Trien ci nghi bai toi la Phe-ro uan nhit cu nghe bai toi la An jo uan Tau (?) Cu nghi bai toy la Tho me cu nghi bai toy la Si le cu nghi bay toy la Lu i si cu nghi bai toy la Phi	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:aa3e621d38be2379cd2b9db9ef8d620b", "default:extract:8119268568033ee1d58153cbb68fa6c7"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:27
chunk-42eda42988ba1c62115a06b13931a7cb	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	74	800	nam.\n\nTruroc khi cac cha Dong Ten dén truyén-giao, nghia la tir nim 1615 tr? vé truoc, chung ta gap nhung tir-ngir, nhing kiéu n6i chua du kha-nang dien-dat thyc-chat Cong-giao. Ngontir luc bay gio chua di kip noi-dung muon pho-dien.\n\nNo lurc truyén-giao cia cac Cha Dong Tén trong tien-ban thé-ky XVI1 da phat-dong mot cuoc tién-h6a vuot burc trong ngon-ngtr Cong-giao Viet-Nam. Thira-hu?ng kinh-nghiem ngonngir Cong-giao Trung-hoa, cam-thong sau-sac voi tinh-than Viet-ngir, cac thira-sai voi can-ban than-hoc virng-vang va cac giao-dan v6i trinh-do giao-ly kha-quan va durc-tin song dong, da cung nhau gop cong chuyén-dich, sang-che danh-tir, thi-\n\nnghiem trau.doi 16i pho-dien. Két-qua la c6 mot s6 danh-tir bi dao-thai, nhieu danh-tir dugc cong-nhan. Loi dung-ngir lai Viet lai Au hay hoan-toan chiu anh-hu?ng Han-van chi la bien-phap tam-thoi dap-irng nhu-cau cap-bach (26). Trong n6. lurc xay-durng ngon-ngir Cong-giao Viet-Nam, chung ta nhan thay khuynh-huong phat-huy cong-giao tinh va dan-toc tinh dan da thang the.\n\nD6 la duong-huong tién-trién ma chung ta nhan thay trong nhurng van-lieu gibi-thieu trén day va nhat la trong cac tac-pham chu quoc-ngir cua Alexandre de Rhodes.\n\n- (26) Cac sach bon cac Dja-phan Bac- Viet deu co chép ban kinh Han-vani\n2. quen goi la Kinh Cau Chu. Chung toi phong-doan kinh nay thong-dung tir thoi-ky so-khai cia giao-hoi Cong-giso Viet-Nam.\n\nKinh cau chtr\n\nThien-Chua cang lan than dang.\n\nThura : Kirixito cang lan than dang.\n\nKirixito ph& thinh than dang. .\n\nThien-Chua cang lan thän dang.\n\nThura : Kirixito thuy don than dang.\n\nThua : Cong lon thon dang.\n\nTai thien Thien Chua phy gia\n\nThuc the Thien Chua tir gia.\n\nThanh Than Thien Chua gia\n\nThanh Maria\n\nTam vi nhat the Thien Chua gia.\n\nThua : Vi thän dang cäu\n\nDong than chi thanh dong than gia?\n\nThien-Chua thanh mau\n\nKirixito chi mau\n\n(Xem tiep trang 131)\n\nThuy thai Vo nhiém nguyen toi chl hau.\n\nChi thanh Man coi chi hau\n\nAn-hoa chi hau.\n\nTrir mien the toi Thien Chua duong cao gia.\n\nThua : Chua xa thon dang.\n\nTrir mien the toi Thien Chua duong cao gia.\n\nThua : Chua lan than dang.\n\nThien than lai bao Thanh Mau Maria nai nhan Thanh Than thy dung thinh chung dong dao khan ky Thien Chua, di Chua th6nh sung ph6 u thau dang linh hon (hay la linh hon mo). Ti than pham do Thien than chi b6o di chi Thien Chua tir giang duyng gia, nhan ky kho nan cap ky thap tur Thanh gia hanh dai ur phuc sinh chi vinh phuc, die	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:76a3bf60807db7287bdd254d8e2b8f30", "default:extract:663055c1985f27d0f24307f5d632fdfd"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:34
chunk-d221810f9603abddb56c15cfdfa207e8	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	78	800	-nguyen nhat-tung cuing da la la nhtng cung ngan-nga khi doc sach Thanh trong nha tho, nhtrng cung-dieu tram-bong nhip-nhang. Cao hon mot bac nra. nhirng dieu bi-ai doc trong mua Thuong-Kh6, nhing bai vevan kinh ming Sinh Nhat va dang tien Durc Ba. Tat ca déu tham-nhuan hon nhac loi tho c6-truyén cua dan-toc va songdong dirc tin sot-sang.\n\nDac-sac hon hét la nhing bai Van Dang Hoa, tong-hgp ba nghe-thuat'thi, vu, nhac trong niem kinh mén Durc Me. Nha nhac-hoc Chuong-Thi, da gibi-thieu phan tinh-tuy cua Van Dang Hoa nhu sau :\n\nα Ngay xua, khong ai biét tur doi nao, van hoa da lienkét chat-che voi viec ton sung Dirc Me trong thang nam. Vi vay ma c6 nhirng kiéu nbi day y-nghia : α Thang Dirc Ba Thang rioc kieu Dirc Ba, Thang ruoc hoa, Thang dang hoa, Thang hoa. uop  'ou o 'nx  ouo un-a eu l 6oy ooni An the to-chirc, la ngay ai nay t6 1ong sung-kinh Durc Me mot cach phi-thuong: nao két hoa lam kieu, nao moi cac doan-the cua onq nou w oonp ua ann oeo suai tuoo-auo ton uo-ui nx. vui-thu : nao co-quat, nao khan-ao, 1 nao khong mot ngay nao c6. Trung-tam-diem cuoc ruoc chinh la luic dang hoa. Gio-phut kieu hoa vao nha tho va bit dau dang hoa la gio-phut tot do. Ai nay thu het tam-tri vao canh tranghoang cuia nha tho, vao kieu Dirc Me, vao dan con tho-äu dang thay mat goi nguoi α dang hoa dang nén cung long 》 cho. Me nhan-ai. Say-me khong phai vi tan, quat, hoa, nén, khong\n\nphai vi bau khi tung-birng nao-nhiet, khong phai vl dang dieu mém-mai va doan-trang cuia cac con Dirc Me cho bang say-me vi bai Van Dang Hoa. Chinh vi loi ca va cung van lam song dong nhirng mau-sac va. nhing cong-trinh bai-tri lam rungchuyén tam-hon moi nguoi du cuoc. Vi bai van la loi caunguyén c6 nhip-nhang, c6 thu-vi c6 y-nghia turgng-trung ratphong-phu va tinh-cach dac-biet Viet-Nam vay.\n\nα Van Dang Hoa d2 c6 mot lich-sir, da durgc coi nhu 1oi tam-huyét cia tirng the-he Cong-giao dang len truoc toa Durc Me Viet-Nam. Rieng ve phuong-dien am-nhac, van hoa la buoc dau cua nghe-thuat am-nhac Cong-giao Viet-Nam 》 (15)\n\nLoi ca dugc sang-tac theo cac the tho dan-toc nhur n6i 16i, luc bat, thuong gom nhurng tir-nhr co, hay nhing kiéu n6i dac-biet cuia Cong-giao. Cung-dieu rat phong-phu dac-sac co bai la nhtrng dieu ca ly co-truyén, c6 bai durgc α cau-tao theo mot duong l6i riéng-biet, khac	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:6fee93e254fc6f32d29f3f70d1774c79", "default:extract:9a068d4e052e00ac24f2cc414f4cfcc3"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:35
chunk-928aee69df0b8c277262189493d7c180	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	69	800	gia mau va tr? nén thong-dung.\n\nDi-ngon cua mot nguoi da song dao nhu thay giang Anré chirng to rang tieng Viet da bat dau c6 kha-nang dien-dat mot Dao Song.\n\n## VI1.- CONG-THUC RU'A TO1 (1645)\n\nNam 1645, theo de-nghi cuia giao-si Alexandre de Rhodes, 35 giao-si Dong Tén truyen-giao tai Viet-Nam, Trung-hoa va Nhat.ban, nh6m-hop duoi quyen chu-toa cua giao-si Cabrol de thao-luan va quyet-nghi vé cong-thurc rira toi bang Viet-ngu.\n\nTheo linh-muc Nguyen Khac-Xuyén, bien-ban hoi-nghi nay con luru-tri tai Vien Bio Tang Dong Tén ? Roma duoi ky-hieu ARSI Jap. Sin 80ff 35-39 (20)\n\nLinh-muc Thanh-Lang kham-pha rang d6 la ban turongtrinh cua giao-si Marini viét nam l654 g?i cho P.Assislente de Portugal d' thuat lai hoi-nghi nam 1645 αduoi hinh-thirc mot bien-ban, trang thr nhat c6 the coi la tieu-dan (viet nam 1654) de gibi-thieu bien-ban da lam nam 1645》 (21).\n\nDu viét nam 1645 hay sau lai nam 1654, van-kien ve cong- thirc rira toi cung la mot chirng-tich ve danh-tir cong-giao nam 1645.\n\nTheo La-ngi, cong-thirc rira toi la: Ego te baptizo in nomine Patris, et Filli, et Spiritus sancti. Cong-thirc nay khong bat-buoc phai doc bang la-ngir nén cac thira-sai cong-giao da dich ra tieng dia-phuong dé de hieu. Nhung dich-thuat khong phai\n\n(20) Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, bdd, xem sach nay, trang II1 chu 10 churong ll.\n\n(21) Thanh-Lang, Nhcng chng durong cuia chi viet quoc-ngv, in trong Dai hoc s6 19, thang 3-1961 trang 22.\n\nI. de-dang vi can phai dat y La-ngr va thich-irng voi tinh-than vA cu-phap tieng dia-phuong.\n\nO Trung-hoa, viec sir-dung cong-thirc rura toi trai qua ba B0 : Nga tay nhir nhan Patele, cap Feilio, cap Spiritu santo danh giai-doan : truoc la dung La-ngir, sau la ghep chur Han va chu gid, sau cung Ia dung toan chr Han : a Nga tay nhir nhan Phu, cip Ti, cap Thanh Than chi danh》 (22).\n\nO Viet-Nam, cong-thirc dugc cong-nhan trong thoi-ky nay chi con hai tieng ngoai-lai : (spirito santo) : α Tao rira mai nhen Danh cha va con va Spirito santo) (phién-dien theo chinh-ta ngay nay la : Tao rira may nhan danh cha va con va Spirito Santo).\n\nCuoc thao-luan rat soi-noi ve tir-ngir nhan danh va cac quan-diem dugc phat-bieu la tai-lieu giup chung ta hiéu-biet v tinh-hinh ngon-ngr Cong-giao luc bay gio.\n\nDao Cong-giao tin rang chi c6 mot Thien-Chua nhung imot Thien-Chua Ba Ngoi. Dieu quan-he la phai n6i the nao dé hiéu ro la mot Thien	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:5f57ae0327d5fab6817e0ec0ecea41f4", "default:extract:476870216aacb502bd998b5c2b213e45"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:36
chunk-22d9bd8b3da08bb0c69318f9eea2f2b4	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	80	800	) thanh, Chung toi dang tam long (i) thanh,\n\nMay loi van phic (i) may nganh (a) may nganh Man-coi (i).\n\n<!-- image -->\n\nVan-hoc-sir va nhac-sir Viet-Nam khong the bo qua truyén-thong ca-nhac phung-vu binh-dan. Gan day cong cuoc suru-tam (19) va phat-trién (20) nen ca-nhac ay da dugc dat eoy-uea in-eig Sunuu H-Anp ouy-uonuy guon ap-uea queu dan-toc va qui-dinh duong-huong sang-tac moi. Turu-trung,: nha nhac-hoc Chuong-Thi dä dua mot nhan-dinh xac-dang ve gia-tri van-nghe va ton-giao cuia nhirng cung-dieu ca-van. Cong-giao co-truyén :\n\n- α Day d6 nguoi ta ca-tung cac cung sach, cac le-nghi a-phung-vu (para-liturgique) nhu ngam durng cua ta, nhat la d6i voi nhing nguoi da c6 dip so-sanh cac le-nghi ton-giao Dong Tay. Dung y-phuc dai-tang va giong kh6c lam-ly kia dé kh6c Chua Gie-su toi ngay chiu chet, dung cung-giong. diu-dang va nhrng van tho uyén-chuyén kia de vao hang-da\n- kinh mirng Chua Hai-Dong mot ve Sinh-Nhat, cing nhu dang\n- (19) Xem Tim hieu giao-nhac cua Nguyen Khac-Xuyen va Van turc Ba cua Chuong-Thi. Theo ch6 chung toi bi&t, nhac-si Le-quang Nhac, giao-su Truong Quoc-Gia Am-nhac va Kich-nghe Hue da hoan-thanh mot bo sach phan tich nhac-ngir va suu-tap giao-nhac co-truyen Viet-Nam.\n- (20) Theo sur tiet-lo cua H.V.H (bdd), < ai cung mong rang roi ra se co nheng. cupc thi Dang hoa to-chuc mbi nam khong nhung o Sai-gon ma con o nhiéu dja-phan khac. Va nhur vay so bai ban co-truyen tat phai khai-théc het. Cuoc tro vi nguon d6 vira phu-hop vbi tinh-than Cong-dong Vatican Il vira hoa nhip voi phongstrao khao-ciru co-nhac ma Trurong Quoc-Gia Am-nhac dang tien-hanh va mot nhac-si da thurc-nghiem mot cach thanh cong trong nhung bai tan-nhac. Ke thi ngay tir 1948,gi6i nhac si Conggiao da tim ra hirbng di do va da gat-hai duoc ket-qua ben-vung, chung " cb la trong cupc thi vora ke nhieu bai tan-tao da xen ke voi bai cotruyen ma van gay duoc ve hoa-hiep ty-nhien > (Nhat-bao Xay-Dyng. ngay 6-6-1965).\n\nkinh Durc Me hien-vinh mot cung luc bat va nganh hoa ngu .sac, d6 la nhirng le-phép giau y-nghia 'cing nhu giau cam-tinh, co tan-tinh cua con chau Tién-Rong muon dang-tien Thien-Chua sirc kich-dong tam-hon chung ta rat manh, d6 la sy thanh-kinh tat ca nhirng gl minh c6 ) (21)\n\n## 2. Giao-s'r dien-ca.\n\nPhong-trao ca-n	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:871d2260135d9c81c7f6f3c3d5e34880", "default:extract:e3b9377101b43ad83137e639fb55c463"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:45
