chunk-7c8fc5be0d9eba4a73418c30972e474a	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	81	800	hoa ngu .sac, d6 la nhirng le-phép giau y-nghia 'cing nhu giau cam-tinh, co tan-tinh cua con chau Tién-Rong muon dang-tien Thien-Chua sirc kich-dong tam-hon chung ta rat manh, d6 la sy thanh-kinh tat ca nhirng gl minh c6 ) (21)\n\n## 2. Giao-s'r dien-ca.\n\nPhong-trao ca-nhac binh-dan con vugt kh?i pham-vi cac giao-duong ma pho-bien khap noi. Nhirng de-tai trong giao-sir dugc soan thanh loi tho, ph6 thanh dieu nhac truyen-tung khap nu?c.\n\nNam l622, ba chi cua Chua Dang Trong xin chiu phép rira toi. Ba thurong nghe nhrng ban hat dao va tiéu-sir cac thanh do mot nir ca-si Dang Ngoai trinh-bay (22).\n\nGiao-si Alexandre de Rhodes c6 ke lai truong-hgp cua ba Catarina, em gai Chua Trinh Trang: αBa dat thanh tho-van tat ca lich-sr dao Cong-giao bat dau tir tao thien lap dia den khi Chua xuong the lam nguoi, doi song, cuoc tir-nan, phuc-sinh va lén troi cua Ding Ciru-the, Chua Gie-su Ki-to, Chua chung ta va ? cuoi con phu them doan ke chuyen chung toi dén xur Dong-Kinh va cong cuoc truyen-giao ? d6. Ba lam rat hay. Den sau van con dugc tat ca nguoi c6 dao truyén tung cho nhau, ho ngam lén luc lam viec ? nha, luc lam viec ngoai dong\n\n(21) Chuong Thi, Van Durc Ba, sdd. trang 7.\n\n(22) Japsln 71.462 (chu-thich cua G.S.)\n\nhay luc di duong. Nguoi biet ca-nhac con hoa nhac them vao.\n\nRoi chang nhing nguoi c6 dao ma con ca nhing nguoi khong c6 dao cung thich ngam-vinh. Nho nhirng tho-van d6 ma nhieu ngudi da tr? lai dao 》 (23).\n\nNgoai nhirng dieu trén day, chung ta chua biet gi hon vé cac tac-pham cong-giao truyén-khau dau mua. Chung ta hyvong rang roi day cac nha khao-co se phat-giac dugc chinh van cuon giao-sir dien-ca cua ba Catarina. Tac-pham nay luc dau luu-truyén theo l6i truyen-kh?u nhung c6 1e ve sau dugc chép thanh van va chac dugc luru-trir trong thu-vien cac co- quan Cong-giao hay lang quen trong tai-lieu cua tu-gia.\n\n## 11.- HUNG-BIEN TON-GIAO\n\nTheo giao-sir, cac giao-si Dong Tén truyen giao ? VietNam trong tien-ban the-ky XVII phan dong déu thong-thao Viet-ngr va giang dao truc tiép bang tieng Viet. Doi-thoai voi nguoi ngoai-dao, dien-giai Phuc-Am cho giao - hiu, huan. luyén than-hoc cho thay-giang, d6 la nhing trach-vu giao-muc cap-bach ddi hoi cac giao-si phai tr? tai hung-bien bang Vietngu. Ve phän giao-dan, y-thirc tong-do phat-sinh tir diurc tin chom no nhung nhiet-thanh da the-hien trong	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:ad2909bf1d73d88de1d39609b244ea38", "default:extract:72abbabd259091e5f051ff2f2f1d0b8a"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:31:46
