ng 39-40.\n\ntrong dao cong-giao nhu nhtng tin-dieu ve Thien-Chua sang tao, Thién-Chua quan-phong. Thien-Chua thu?ng-phat loai nguoi xrng voi phuc-toi cua moi nguoi. Thién-Chua giangsinh ciru-chuoc loai nguoi, Thien-Chua giang-sanh trong long mot nir αdong-than), thu thong thu kho thu hinh thap tr, song Van-de linh-hon cung durgc ban giai ky-cang. Phep bi-tich rira lai, len troi va ngay	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:b196ef5ed2794ddc2648227f9526a171", "default:extract:9c0bb02bfc75232413867aa6feedb57e"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:07
chunk-980cd0aaf6912a718dd4b450857535f1	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	89	800	sach nhung mot suy-luan gian-di dua dén két-luan d6 la cuon sach cua Minh-kien xuat-ban ? Trung-hoa nam 1584. Cau chuyén xiy ra vao khoang cu6i nam 1627 dau nam l628, luc giao-si moi den Dang Ngoai. Thay sai da gitr sach d6 30 nam turc la sach ay phai mang ve truoc nam 1598. Giao-si Minh-kien da gip than-sinh thay sai nam 1585 va cuon sach trao tang di nhien la cuon Thién-Chua thyc-luc chinh-van in nam 1584.\n\nDoan trich-dan trén day con cho chung ta. biet rang giaosi Alexandre de Rhodes va co le cac giao-si khac cung vay, c6 mang dén dat Viet cac sach giao-ly Han-van de pho-bien. Hon nura, l6i giang-dao cia giao-si da theo dung thur-ty nhu trong sach cua Minh-kién.\n\nMot sir-lieu khac chirng-to cuon Thien-Chua Thrc-nghia (1603) cua giao-si Ricci (Lgi-ma-dau) da la co-hoi thuc day cu Phao-lo Quang-Nam tr? lai dao Cong-giao nam 1622. Cu la c6 vin phap-luat cua hoang-tr tran-thi Quang-Nam doc nhieu sich vé dao-ly kim-co, nhung chua c6 tac-pham nao lam cu vira long. Sau khi nghe giao-si Pina thuyét-giao va doc sach cia Lgi-ma-dau, cu n6i chac tim thay dao that. Sau ram thang gieng nam ay cu da to-churc tiec moi cac quan chirc, trinh-bay ly do cu theo dao Cong-giao va cu cing da to-chirc hoi-hop de nghe cha Pina thuyet-giao (4)\n\n(4) Xem Bartoli, Historia della Compania di Gesu Vol. V trang 207-222.\n\nLai theo Pfister (5), cuon sach bon chtr Han cua giao-sl P. Soerio in nam 1601 & Trung-hoa c6 le da dugc dich ra qu6cam va ph6-bién nam 1631.\n\nN6i ve anh-hu?ng cua cac sach giao-ly chr Han luru-hanh chung ta c6 the dong y v6i giao-si André Mariller (6) nhu sau1\n\nα D%i voi cac tan-tong nguoi Viet cung nhr doi voi cac thira-sai rao giang Phuc-Am, cong-trinh van-hoc pho-dien dirc tin thyc-hién ? Trung-hoa duong nhr da dong vai trd congnhan hon la anh-huong tryc tiép, chi-phoi toan bo. Kham-pha su d6ng gop quan-trong cua nhtrng dinh-che va tin-ngu?ng Trung-hoa, cac thra-sai deu xem nguoi Viet la mot dan-toc doc-sang, nen trong khi tiép-xuc' voi nguoi Viet Dang Ngoai va Dang Trong, cac ngai tu-do tim-kiem mot phuong-phap thong-khao va mot ngon-ngr pho-dien thich-hgp. Vu-tru tinhthan va dao-dirc ma cac thira-sai nhan thay bieu-lo trong cac tu-si Phat-giao, nho-si, quan-chirc cung nhu quan-nhan, thythuyen va nong-dan, co nhieu diém tuong-ty voi the-gioi tutu?ng Trung-Hoa. Va nhung vi tong-do ay cung soi-noi mot	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:b2f521346aa2584543923db7339931af", "default:extract:585d028840c215877afa98c28932926b"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:07
chunk-228ea2b83c7801849a3cba6bab663185	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	92	800	de Rhodes cuing soan tur-dien va vanpham nhw Didaco, chi khac la trong luic Didaco soan mot cuon giao-ly thrc-hanh thi Alexandre de Rhodes da soan mot tacpham ly-thuyét sau rong hon.\n\nMuon nhan xét dai-cuong ve gia-tri cac sach giao-ly Nhatbin noi tren, chung ta can biet qua tinh hinh giang-day giaoly vao the ky XVI XVI1. O Bo.dao-nha, luc bay gio dugc coi nhu la mot trung-tam truyen-giao, c6 mot giao-si da viét hai cuon giao-ly : mot cuon dai goi la gido-ly dien-giai (Symboli fidei Declaratio) va mot goi la giio-ly dqi-cuong (Doctrina). Cuon sau nay dugc pho-bien rong-rai ? cac mien truyén-giao vao the-ky XVI, da tung dugc phién-dich sang tieng tamoul, tiéng Ma-lai, tiéng Nhat viét theo I6i romaji.\n\nNguyen Khac-Xuyén c6 phan-tich cuon Doctrina bang romaji in ? Amacusa nam 1592 lam thi-du :\n\nα Truoc het la cach-thirc lam dau thanh-gia roi toi may kinh can-thiet hay thong-dung trong Ki-to-giao : Kinh lay Cha, Kinh kinh ming, Kinh than lai Nr-vrong, Kinh Tin. Kinh sau d6 toi muoi gioi-ran Thién-Chua, sau gioi-ran Hoi-thanh va cu?i-cung la nhung dieu hieu-biet ve toi nang toi nhe, bay phép bi-tich, cac nhan-dirc gom c6 : bay m?i toi däu, bay cong viec phuc-dirc, bon nhan-dirc ca, ba nhan-durc doi-than, bay on Dirc Chua Thanh-Than, tam m?i phuic that, Kinh cao minh... (9)\n\nNhung sach giao-ly voi noi-dung so-sai, kho-khan nhu the khong thich-hop voi nhung dan-toc c6 mot nén van-h6a c6-truyén ? A-Dong. Do d6, c6 phong-trao sang-tac sách giaoly sau-sac linh-dong hon de tang-gia hieu-lurc truyén-giao bang cach gioi-thieu day-du dao Cong-giao la mot dao mac- khai khac han cac ton-giao ? A-Dong.\n\n## III.— CONG - TRINH VAN -HOC CONG-GIAO TRUNG-HOA\n\nsou-uea guon eou-aunin ooy-uea eno dog guop is.\n\nViet-Nam la mot syr-kien hien-nhien. Trong truong-hop vanhoc Cong-giao, dieu dang noi la nhirng tac-pham chr Han da gay anh-hu?ng ? Viet-Nam la cong-trinh cua nhirng giaosi truyén-giao ? Trung Hoa.\n\n(9) Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, Quan-diem than-hoc trong phep giang tam ngay cua giao-si Dac-lo. ba: trong Dai-hoc so 19 thang 2, 1961.\n\n## 1. Cong-trinh phien-am Hoa-ngur.\n\nCuon ngir-vung hay tur-dien Bo-Hoa dau-tien la congtrinh cua hai giao-si Dong Tén, Micae Rrggieri (Minh-kién) va Matteo Ricci (Lgi-ma-dau) vao khoang nhurng nam 15841588. Theo Nguyen Khac.Xuyén (l0	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:6f19e6c789fddd517dafe5a752bb1a14", "default:extract:cfe4878e4bae168744e7da07569200bd"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:09
