chunk-397d0676481d20aec8b4d2553afdb6af	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	105	800	ta phai ke Girolamo Majorica la inot trong nhtrng nha van dau tién viet tan-van chu Nom.\n\nBut-phap cua Girolamo Majorica tu-nhién thanh-thyc, nghi sao viét vay, khong dung deo-got trau-chuot loi van :\n\nα Ong Thanh Y-na-xu chiu kho be ngoai lam vay, nhung\n\n- ma trong linh-hon cang chiu kh6 nura. Vi dém ngay bankhoan, nhürng lo chang hay I Dirc Chua Loi tha toi hay la chua, thi'nguoi lam het sirc cho dugc khoi sy ngo trong long ay, vi b?i chura dugc yén.long, thi toan an chay tron doi cho dén khoi su 1oi trong longn (26).\n\nLoi ke chuyen cua Girolamo Majorica rat linh-dong, ngon-ngr cua nguoi trong chuyen dugc tuong-thuat dé giup ta hieu dugc tam-tu va hanh-dong:\n\n- α Ban dem· du ma gia rét thi Ong thanh Y-na-xu nam trén van khong ma thirc suy-nghi su Dirc Chua Loi. Khi nguoi do nha ay ten la Giu-ong. he la dem thi ong thanh Y-na-xu khien Giu-ong di nam truoc. Ma Giu-ong c6 nhieu lan lam thinh, rinh-ng6 ma xem, ben ong thay thanh Y-na-xu\n\nkhi quy goi, khi sap minh xuong dat khi ngia mat lén, ma thay nguoi noi 1én khong, chan khoi (?) (?) ? mat mui c6 haoquang sang lang ma than-th? cing Dirc Chua Loi rang :α Chua chra long toi, cho gi thien-ha biét Durc Chua toi ma tho v.\n\n- α C6 ké thay mat mui ong thanh Y-na-xu chang phai ke mon, thi mang nguoi rang : sao ong, ong di an may lam vay. hay la c6 lam sy loi chi trong ma hoac nguoi ta bat minh thi n, gia chuoc vay chang ?\n\nα Khi nguoi ta mang lam vay thi ong thanh Y-na-xu nghenh c6 tr? lai, vui'mat ma nghe het loi ay doan moi tra loi rang : α O'n ong lam phuc cho toi ) (27).\n\nSu ngac-nhien cua Giu-ong, moi thic-mac cia nhitrng nguoi thay ong thanh Y-na-xu kho-lhanh, cuoc doi tan-hién va tamly khiem-nhuong cua ong thanh Y-na-xu, bay nhiéu su viec va tam-tur da durgc dien-ta trong mot doan ngan voi nhtirng chi-tiet song-dong.\n\n## 5.- Gia.tri\n\nChung ta nhan thay vin-pham cua Girolamo Majorica hoan-toan phuc-vu muc-tiéu truyen-giao va tu-dirc voi nhtrng de-tai rut trong giao-ly, thanh-sir. Dao-giao da chi-ph?i nghéthuat trong van-phäm cua Girolamo Majorica. D6 la nhtrng van-kien quy-bau giup chung ta tim hiéu phuong-phap giang dao, ngon-ngtr cong-giao trong tien-ban the-ky XVII.\n\n(27) sdd. oan thi 7 : Ong Thanh I-na-xu di hoc cung chju kho o thanh Sai-lo-na. Phan trich-dan chinh-van deu phien-dien tir nguyen-van chu Nom.\n\n## II.— GIOAN THANH-MINH (1588	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:f95bde3facd06f30d184a1ce683a0c3b", "default:extract:7efa6b2db3f89541f8160517813a4b0a"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:25
