ham chr Han cua Micae Ruggerio (Minh-kién) xuat-ban nam 1584 tai Phuc-kien.\n\n## Sach gom co muoi sau chuong :\n\n- : Chan hiru nhat vi Thién Chua (chi co mot\n- Chuong I Thien-Chua that).\n- Churong I1 : Thien Chua su tich (nhung dac-tinh cua Thién-\n- Chua).\n- Chuong III  : Giai thich the nhan.. Thien-Chua (luan ve sy\n- loai nguoi tim-hieu Thien-Chua).\n- Chuong VI  : Th	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:13021dd1eddfa70e9bb4400ffa500576", "default:extract:d9e1c90eef5d9894b21fa116c6ecbbb2"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:26
chunk-7d22c25ce2e2c5d404366c84d36ca901	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	98	800	. Tir viec dich-thuat dén viec sang-tac, cac tac-gia sach giao-ly Nhat-ban va Trung-hoa da bieu-thi hai khuynh-huong vin-hoc : mot la van dung 16i phien am La-tinh, hai la van-dung van-tr co-truyen. Hai khuynhhuong nay cung xuat-hien ? Viet-Nam voi hai loai tac-pham : tac-pham bang chir quoc-ngir va tac-pham bang chu Nom.\n\n## CHUONGV\n\n## VAN.HQC CONG-GIAO CHU NOM\n\nSu tr? lai cua nhirng nho-si va tu-si Phat-giao la mot yéut6 phat-trien van-hoc cong-giao. Cac tan-tong nay da giup cac thira-sai ghi chép bang chtr nom nhtrng van-kien cong-giao can-thiét. Giao-si Alexandre de Rhodes, khi moi dén xr Bac da nho mot thay do chép nhirng kinh toi som va kinh muoi dieu ran (l). Chac cac thay giang cing ghi-chép nhirng le-luat do cac cha an-dinh cho to-chirc tong-do giao-dan tien khoi ma cac thay la nhung can-bo dac-lurc (2). C6 sach chép rang trong\n\n- (1) Xem Nguyen Hong, Lich-sir truyen giao o Viet-Nam sdd. Ve trurong hop cha doc cho de nhing nguoi tan-tong theo d6 ma hoc》 (trg 105).\n2. tro lai cua su cy Gioakim & An-virc, tac-gia viet: αKhong dem phien cu. cha Dac-lo nho mot thanh-nien biet chi chep ra chir nom nhing kinh Ve truong-hop giang dao cho nguroi phong-hui & lang Van-no, toc-gia viét : *Trong so d6 co ong Simon, mot nguroi c6 chi-nghia. Duoc cha Dic-lo goi cho mot ban kinh muroi gibi-ran Chua, ong lien dem day cho cac ngudi hui trong lang va ngay chi-nhat vi khong the dén nha tho duroc, nhing lang hui hop nhau lai trubc anh Chua va doc.cac kinh d6 v6i nhau : (trg 106).\n- (2) Xem Phan Phat Huon, Viet-Nam giao-sir, I, trg 77.\n\nluc vang cac cha, cac thay da soan mot cuon lich cong-giao de nhac-nh? giao-dan vé cac tiet- 1e Cong-giao (3). Cha Onuphre Borges be trén Phai-doan Truyén-giao Dang Ngoai tir nam 1656, c6 soan mot tac-pham huan-luyen cac thay-giang, giang-giai cach day bon cho nguoi tan-tong cach giup ke liet va rira toi khi can-kip (4). Ngay dén cuon Phep gidng 8 ngay cua giao-si Alexandre de Rhodes trong thoi-ky con la so -thao cing da dugc ghi chép bang chr nom va chr quoc-ngir de cac thay- giang va giao-dan tien-dung (5).\n\nPhong-trao van-hoc cong-giao chtr nom la mot nhu-cau -oud Key yuip-ug oonp enyo nsu-onb nuo oni suon ai-oiy bin rong-rai. Ve nhung tac-pham ke tren day, dugc nhac-Ans ns iou suon keu es-nui oo eno nenu-y ogo duon ouu lu	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:4547ec4d3d252b502da6c478fe988115", "default:extract:ca9f1e2f59cd97b0fb2a30c9ecca9b3c"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:32:27
