chunk-2f8b61a1827fb9ae6f69fb22acc28eaf	fb6bf22d-c347-46d4-8dae-e5b46327437b	doc-3092ba448fe8a518793032dd6f30ec1e	152	800	va di-doan ngau-turgng khac (20)\n\nTheo phuong-phap trén day, tac-gia da lgi-dung nhirng gia-tri van-h6a ton-giao tich-cuyc cua dan-toc Viet-Nam de trinh bay mot giao-ly moi. Mot mat khac, tac-gia tuan theo le-16i giang-dao co-truyén cua giao-hoi la keu goi van-dung ly-tri de suy-luan nhung van de-cao su ph6-thac trong nguyen-cau khiém-nhuong, trinh-bay giao-ly nhung van thuc day giaohru tim hieu.\n\nSau cung chung ta cing nén xét thai-do cia tac-gia d6 voi cac tin-ngu?ng ton-giao khac ? Viet-Nam. Tac-gia phan-\n\n(20) Alexandre de Rhodes, Histolre du Tunquin, trang 175 - 178 ; Relazione, trang 173 — 186 ; Tonchinensis Historiac libri duo trang 93 — 94.— Nguyen Khac-Xuyen trich dich, Dai-hoc so 16,trang 47.\n\ntich tinh-vi viec tho kinh thin-linh, cong-nhan nhung gii-tri tich-cuc cua dao Khong, thang-than chi-trich phung phong-tuc di-doan. Ve Phat-gino va Lao-giao, thc-gia to thai-do nghiem khac, mot doi khi co nhieu phan-doin cuc-doan.\n\nVe diém sau nay, Nguyen Khac-Xuyen nhan-xet : α Nhtrng phan-doin cia Dic Lo ve cac ton-giao, mot phin da chiu anhhurong' cua mot khoa than-hoc bung-bit the-ky XVI - XVI1. Theo giao-ly thieu sot nay, (trai voi hoc-thuyet co-truyén, ti 0- ieosu yun (a-i y a den-H iyd-og oeo eno mqu giao, chi c6 sai-lam ve viec cia ta-ma qui-quai trong het cac tongiáo khac. Chung toi khong bao phan-doan nay sai laim song khong hoan-toan duing. Day la mot phan-doin mot chieu, di xa co-truyén Phuc-Am, cac tong-do va cac giao-phu. Boi vay, c6 the n6i dirgc ring cac nha truyen-gio thoi xua chura duroc sura-soan day-du d' tim-hiéu, cam-thong voi cac ton-giao khac.\n\nα Ngay nay, nguroi Ki-to-giao co mot thai-ao khac voi thai-do c6 the nbi durgc la thieu-sot cia cac nha truyén-giio the-ky XVI-xVI1. Cac luan-dieu qua gay-gat va α doc-doan 》 khong con thich-hop va khong dugc cong-nhan. D6 la diell phai 1e。 (2 1)\n\nNhrng nguoi ngoai cong-giao co the chi-trich mot vai phan-doan cia giao-si Alexandre de Rhodes nhung thiét-tu?ng can phai dat cuon α Phep giang tam ngdy 》 trong hoan-canh lichs'r, trong khuon-kh? cuia cac khoa than-hoc va truyén-giao thoi dai cia tac-gia de tranh moi sy hieu-lam c6 the c6 trong hien-tai.\n\n(21) Nguyen Khac-Xuyen, Tac-pham qu6c-ngi dau-tien : Phép giang tam ngay,	lịch-sử-văn-học-công-giáo-việt-nam-pdf-dantocking.com.pdf	["default:extract:8780157cce00bba1e2aebc90452f5887", "default:extract:217cec68d851660ebe4a1485f3fd074a"]	2026-04-10 12:28:45	2026-04-10 12:33:59
